-------------------------0 sample_num
```sql
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM head
WHERE age > 56;
```
-------------------------1 sample_num
```sql
SELECT h.name, h.born_state, h.age
FROM head h
JOIN management m ON h.head_ID = m.head_ID
ORDER BY h.age;
```
-------------------------2 sample_num
```sql
SELECT Creation, Name, Budget_in_Billions
FROM department;
```
-------------------------3 sample_num
```sql
SELECT MAX(Budget_in_Billions) AS Max_Budget, MIN(Budget_in_Billions) AS Min_Budget
FROM department;
```
-------------------------4 sample_num
```sql
SELECT AVG(Num_Employees)
FROM department
WHERE Ranking BETWEEN 10 AND 15;
```
-------------------------5 sample_num
```sql
SELECT h.name
FROM head h
WHERE born_state NOT LIKE '%California%';
```
-------------------------6 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT d.Creation
FROM department d
JOIN head h ON d.Department_ID = (SELECT department_ID FROM management m JOIN head hm ON m.head_ID = hm.head_ID WHERE hm.born_state = 'Alabama' AND m.temporary_acting = 0)
```
-------------------------7 sample_num
```sql
SELECT born_state
FROM head
GROUP BY born_state
HAVING COUNT(name) >= 3;
```
-------------------------8 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM Creation) AS Year,
  COUNT(*) AS Num_Departments
FROM
  department
GROUP BY
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM Creation)
ORDER BY
  Num_Departments DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------9 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.Name, d.Num_Employees
FROM department d
JOIN management m ON d.Department_ID = m.department_ID
JOIN head h ON m.head_ID = h.head_ID
WHERE m.temporary_acting = 'Yes';
```
-------------------------10 sample_num
```sql
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT temporary_acting) AS num_statuses
FROM management;
```
-------------------------11 sample_num
```sql
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT d.Department_ID)
FROM department d
LEFT JOIN head h ON d.Department_ID = h.head_ID
WHERE h.head_ID IS NULL;
```
-------------------------12 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT age
FROM head
WHERE head_ID IN (
  SELECT head_ID
  FROM management
);
```
-------------------------13 sample_num
```sql
SELECT born_state
FROM head
WHERE name IN (
  SELECT name
  FROM head
  WHERE department_ID IN (
    SELECT Department_ID
    FROM department
    WHERE Name IN ('Treasury', 'Homeland Security')
  )
) GROUP BY born_state
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT name) = 2;
```
-------------------------14 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.Department_ID, d.Name, COUNT(h.head_ID) AS num_heads
FROM department d
JOIN head h ON d.Department_ID = h.department_ID
GROUP BY d.Department_ID, d.Name
HAVING COUNT(h.head_ID) > 1;
```
-------------------------15 sample_num

FROM head
WHERE name LIKE '%Ha%';

FROM city c

GROUP BY c.Official_Name
HAVING COUNT(fc.Competition_ID) > 1;
```

-------------------------56 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.course_name, COUNT(s.student_id) AS registered_students
FROM Student_Course_Registrations s
JOIN Courses c ON s.course_id = c.course_id
GROUP BY c.course_name
ORDER BY registered_students DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------57 sample_num
```sql

FROM Courses c
JOIN Student_Course_Registrations scr ON c.course_id = scr.course_id
GROUP BY c.course_name
ORDER BY COUNT(scr.student_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------58 sample_num
```sql

LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------59 sample_num

FROM Student_Course_Registrations s

  SELECT sc.student_id
  FROM Student_Course_Registrations sc
  GROUP BY sc.student_id
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) ASC
  LIMIT 1
)

-------------------------81 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.course_name, COUNT(s.student_id) AS registered_students
FROM Student_Course_Registrations sc
JOIN Courses c ON sc.course_id = c.course_id
JOIN Students s ON sc.student_id = s.student_id
GROUP BY c.course_name;
```
-------------------------82 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    scr.course_id,
    c.course_name,
    COUNT(scr.student_id) AS registered_students
FROM
    Student_Course_Registrations scr
JOIN
    Courses c ON scr.course_id = c.course_id
GROUP BY
    scr.course_id, c.course_name
ORDER BY
    scr.course_id;
```

-------------------------93 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT a.city
FROM Addresses a
JOIN People_Addresses pa ON a.address_id = pa.address_id
JOIN People p ON pa.person_id = p.person_id
JOIN Students s ON p.person_id = s.student_id
WHERE p.person_type = 'Student';
```
-------------------------94 sample_num
```
SELECT DISTINCT city
FROM Addresses
JOIN People_Addresses ON Addresses.address_id = People_Addresses.address_id
JOIN People ON People_Addresses.person_id = People.person_id
JOIN Students ON People.person_id = Students.student_id;
```

-------------------------103 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.student_id, s.student_details, c.course_name, sc.registration_date
FROM Students s
JOIN Student_Course_Registrations sc ON s.student_id = sc.student_id
JOIN Courses c ON sc.course_id = c.course_id
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM Student_Course_Attendance sa
  WHERE sa.student_id = s.student_id AND sa.course_id = sc.course_id
);
```
-------------------------104 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.first_name, p.middle_name, p.last_name, s.student_details
FROM Students s
JOIN People p ON s.student_id = p.person_id
WHERE s.student_id NOT IN (
    SELECT student_id
    FROM Student_Course_Attendance
)
AND s.student_id IN (
    SELECT student_id
    FROM Student_Course_Registrations
);
```

  zip_code,

FROM
  weather
WHERE

GROUP BY
  zip_code;

-------------------------133 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.name, s.id
FROM station s
JOIN trip t ON s.name = t.start_station_name
WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM t.start_date) = 8
GROUP BY s.name, s.id
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------134 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.name, s.id
FROM station s
JOIN trip t ON s.name = t.start_station_name
WHERE MONTH(t.start_date) = 8
GROUP BY s.name, s.id
ORDER BY COUNT(t.id) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------141 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.id
FROM station s
JOIN status st ON s.id = st.station_id
WHERE s.city = 'San Francisco'
GROUP BY s.id
HAVING AVG(st.bikes_available) > 10;
```
-------------------------142 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.id
FROM station s
WHERE s.city = 'San Francisco'
AND s.id IN (SELECT station_id
             FROM status
             WHERE bikes_available > 10);
```
-------------------------143 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.name, s.id
FROM station s
WHERE s.id IN (
  SELECT st.station_id
  FROM status st
  WHERE st.bikes_available > 14
  GROUP BY st.station_id
  HAVING AVG(st.bikes_available) > 14
)
UNION
SELECT s.name, s.id
FROM station s
WHERE MONTH(s.installation_date) = 12;
```
-------------------------144 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.name, s.id
FROM station s
WHERE s.id IN (
  SELECT st.station_id
  FROM status st
  WHERE st.bikes_available > 14
  UNION ALL
  SELECT t.start_station_id
  FROM trip t
  WHERE MONTH(t.start_date) = 12
)
```
-------------------------145 sample_num
```sql

-------------------------202 sample_num
```sql
SELECT w.date,
       MIN(w.min_temperature_f) AS min_temp,
       MAX(w.max_temperature_f) AS max_temp
FROM weather w
GROUP BY w.date
ORDER BY ABS(MIN(w.min_temperature_f) - MAX(w.max_temperature_f)) ASC
LIMIT 1;

-------------------------285 sample_num
```sql
SELECT UP.name
FROM user_profiles UP
WHERE UP.partitionid IN (
  SELECT f2
  FROM follows
  WHERE f1 IN (
    SELECT uid
    FROM user_profiles
    WHERE name = 'Tyler Swift'
  )
)
AND UP.partitionid IN (
  SELECT f1
  FROM follows
  WHERE f2 IN (
    SELECT uid
    FROM user_profiles
    WHERE name = 'Tyler Swift'
  )
)
AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM follows WHERE f2 = UP.partitionid) > (
  SELECT COUNT(*) FROM follows WHERE f1 = (
    SELECT uid FROM user_profiles WHERE name = 'Tyler Swift'
  )
);
```

  HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
)

JOIN tweets t ON up.uid = t.uid
GROUP BY up.name;
```
-------------------------296 sample_num
```sql
SELECT up.name, up.partitionid
FROM user_profiles up
JOIN tweets t ON up.uid = t.uid
GROUP BY up.name, up.partitionid
HAVING COUNT(t.id) < 2;
```
-------------------------297 sample_num
```sql
SELECT user_profiles.name, COUNT(tweets.id) AS num_tweets
FROM tweets
JOIN user_profiles ON tweets.uid = user_profiles.uid
GROUP BY user_profiles.name
HAVING COUNT(tweets.id) > 1;
```

HAVING COUNT(t.id) > 0;

-------------------------315 sample_num
```sql
SELECT cc.catalog_entry_name
FROM Catalog_Contents cc
JOIN Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes cca ON cc.catalog_entry_id = cca.catalog_entry_id
JOIN Attribute_Definitions ad ON cca.attribute_id = ad.attribute_id
GROUP BY cc.catalog_entry_name
ORDER BY COUNT(cca.attribute_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------316 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.catalog_entry_name
FROM Catalog_Contents c
JOIN Catalog_Contents_Additional_Attributes caa ON c.catalog_entry_id = caa.catalog_entry_id
JOIN Attribute_Definitions ad ON caa.attribute_id = ad.attribute_id
JOIN Catalogs cat ON c.catalog_id = cat.catalog_id
WHERE (caa.attribute_id, ad.attribute_name) IN (
  SELECT attribute_id, attribute_name
  FROM Attribute_Definitions
  GROUP BY attribute_id, attribute_name
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
  LIMIT 1
)
```

-------------------------427 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.name
FROM employee e
WHERE e.eid IN (
  SELECT c.eid
  FROM certificate c
  WHERE c.aid IN (
    SELECT a.aid
    FROM aircraft a
    WHERE a.name = 'Boeing 737-800'
  )
  INTERSECT
  SELECT c.eid
  FROM certificate c
  WHERE c.aid IN (
    SELECT a.aid
    FROM aircraft a
    WHERE a.name = 'Airbus A340-300'
  )
);
```
-------------------------428 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.name
FROM employee e
JOIN certificate c ON e.eid = c.eid
WHERE c.aid IN (
  SELECT a.aid
  FROM aircraft a
  WHERE a.name = 'Boeing 737-800'
  UNION ALL
  SELECT a.aid
  FROM aircraft a
  WHERE a.name = 'Airbus A340-300'
);
```

WHERE a.AllergyType = (SELECT AllergyType FROM Allergy_Type GROUP BY AllergyType ORDER BY COUNT(*) LIMIT 1);

-------------------------458 sample_num
```sql
SELECT AllergyType
FROM Allergy_Type
WHERE AllergyType = (
  SELECT AllergyType
  FROM Allergy_Type
  GROUP BY AllergyType
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) ASC
  LIMIT 1
);

FROM customers c
JOIN invoices i ON c.id = i.customer_id

  FROM invoices i

  LIMIT 10
)
ORDER BY i.total;

-------------------------558 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name
FROM customers c
JOIN invoices i ON c.id = i.customer_id
JOIN invoice_lines il ON i.id = il.invoice_id
WHERE il.id IN (
  SELECT il2.id
  FROM invoice_lines il2
  GROUP BY il2.invoice_id
  ORDER BY SUM(il2.unit_price * il2.quantity) ASC
  LIMIT 10
)
ORDER BY i.total;
```

-------------------------643 sample_num
```sql
SELECT t.name
FROM tracks t
WHERE t.id IN (
  SELECT pt.track_id
  FROM playlist_tracks pt
  WHERE pt.playlist_id IN (
    SELECT p.id
    FROM playlists p
    WHERE p.name = 'Movies'
  )
) AND t.id NOT IN (
  SELECT pt.track_id
  FROM playlist_tracks pt
  WHERE pt.playlist_id IN (
    SELECT p.id
    FROM playlists p
    WHERE p.name = 'music'
  )
);
```
-------------------------644 sample_num
```sql
SELECT t.name
FROM tracks t
WHERE t.id IN (
  SELECT pt.track_id
  FROM playlist_tracks pt
  WHERE pt.playlist_id IN (
    SELECT p.id
    FROM playlists p
    WHERE p.name = 'Movies'
  )
  AND pt.track_id NOT IN (
    SELECT pt2.track_id
    FROM playlist_tracks pt2
    WHERE pt2.playlist_id IN (
      SELECT p.id
      FROM playlists p
      WHERE p.name = 'music'
    )
  )
)
```
-------------------------645 sample_num
```sql
SELECT t.name
FROM tracks t
WHERE EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM playlist_tracks pt
  WHERE pt.track_id = t.id AND pt.playlist_id IN (
    SELECT id FROM playlists WHERE name = 'Movies'
  )
)
AND EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM playlist_tracks pt
  WHERE pt.track_id = t.id AND pt.playlist_id IN (
    SELECT id FROM playlists WHERE name = 'music'
  )
);
```
-------------------------646 sample_num
```sql
SELECT t.name
FROM tracks t
WHERE t.id IN (
  SELECT pt.track_id
  FROM playlist_tracks pt
  WHERE pt.playlist_id IN (
    SELECT p.id
    FROM playlists p
    WHERE p.name IN ('Movies', 'music')
  )
  GROUP BY pt.track_id
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT pt.playlist_id) = 2
)
```

LEFT JOIN Customers_Cards CC ON C.customer_id = CC.customer_id
WHERE CC.card_id IS NULL;

FROM Album a
JOIN Track t ON a.AlbumId = t.AlbumId
JOIN Genre g ON t.GenreId = g.GenreId
WHERE g.Name IN ('Reggae', 'Rock');

-------------------------897 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.Customer_Phone
FROM Available_Policies ap
JOIN (SELECT policy_type_code, COUNT(*) as count
      FROM Available_Policies
      GROUP BY policy_type_code
      ORDER BY count DESC
      LIMIT 1) as most_popular_policy
ON ap.policy_type_code = most_popular_policy.policy_type_code;
```
-------------------------898 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.Customer_Phone
FROM Available_Policies ap
JOIN Customers c ON ap.Customer_Phone = c.Customer_ID
JOIN (
  SELECT policy_type_code, COUNT(*) as count
  FROM Available_Policies
  GROUP BY policy_type_code
  ORDER BY count DESC
  LIMIT 1
) p ON ap.policy_type_code = p.policy_type_code
```

-------------------------924 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.Customer_name
FROM Customers c
JOIN Customers_Policies cp ON c.Customer_ID = cp.Customer_ID
JOIN First_Notification_of_Loss fnol ON cp.Customer_ID = fnol.Customer_ID
JOIN Services s1 ON fnol.Service_ID = s1.Service_ID
JOIN First_Notification_of_Loss fnol2 ON c.Customer_ID = fnol2.Customer_ID
JOIN Services s2 ON fnol2.Service_ID = s2.Service_ID
WHERE s1.Service_name = 'Close a policy' AND s2.Service_name = 'Upgrade a policy';

-------------------------953 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.id, e.name
FROM enzyme e
JOIN (
  SELECT enzyme_id, COUNT(*) as count
  FROM medicine_enzyme_interaction
  WHERE interaction_type = 'activator'
  GROUP BY enzyme_id
  ORDER BY count DESC
  LIMIT 1
) as temp ON e.id = temp.enzyme_id;
```
-------------------------954 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.id, e.name
FROM enzyme e
JOIN (
  SELECT enzyme_id, COUNT(*) as count
  FROM medicine_enzyme_interaction
  WHERE interaction_type = 'activator'
  GROUP BY enzyme_id
  ORDER BY count DESC
  LIMIT 1
) as activator_count
ON e.id = activator_count.enzyme_id;
```

-------------------------967 sample_num
```sql
SELECT m.name, m.Trade_Name
FROM medicine m
WHERE EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM medicine_enzyme_interaction mei
  WHERE mei.medicine_id = m.id
  AND mei.interaction_type IN ('inhibitor', 'activator')
)
GROUP BY m.name, m.Trade_Name
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT mei.interaction_type) = 2;
```
-------------------------968 sample_num

FROM medicine m

  SELECT 1
  FROM medicine_enzyme_interaction mei
  WHERE mei.medicine_id = m.id AND mei.interaction_type = 'inhibitor'
) AND EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM medicine_enzyme_interaction mei
  WHERE mei.medicine_id = m.id AND mei.interaction_type = 'activator'
);

LIMIT 1;
```

FROM representative
GROUP BY Party
HAVING COUNT(Representative_ID) >= 3;

  FROM representative r2
  WHERE r2.Party = r.Party
  AND r2.State = 'Pennsylvania'
)

FROM member m
LEFT JOIN member_attendance ma ON m.Member_ID = ma.Member_ID
WHERE ma.Member_ID IS NULL;
```

  JOIN course c ON t.course_id = c.course_id
  WHERE c.dept_name = 'Biology'
);
```
-------------------------1454 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.dept_name, COUNT(s.ID) AS total_students, COUNT(i.ID) AS total_instructors
FROM department d
LEFT JOIN student s ON d.dept_name = s.dept_name
LEFT JOIN instructor i ON d.dept_name = i.dept_name
GROUP BY d.dept_name;
```

  a.account_id,
  COUNT(ft.transaction_id) AS transaction_count
FROM
  Financial_Transactions ft
  INNER JOIN Accounts a ON ft.account_id = a.account_id
GROUP BY
  a.account_id;
```
-------------------------1580 sample_num
```sql

FROM Financial_Transactions
GROUP BY account_id;
```

-------------------------1708 sample_num
```sql
SELECT u.name, i.i_id
FROM item i
JOIN (SELECT i.i_id, AVG(r.rank) AS avg_rank
      FROM review r
      GROUP BY r.i_id
      ORDER BY avg_rank DESC
      LIMIT 1) AS top_ranked_item
ON i.i_id = top_ranked_item.i_id
JOIN useracct u ON i.i_id IN (SELECT r.i_id
                               FROM review r
                               WHERE r.u_id = u.u_id)
```

-------------------------1712 sample_num

  ORDER BY avg_trust DESC
  LIMIT 1
) t
WHERE u.u_id = t.source_u_id;
```
-------------------------1713 sample_num
```sql

  u.name,
  AVG(trust.trust) AS avg_trust
FROM
  trust
  JOIN useracct u ON trust.target_u_id = u.u_id
GROUP BY
  u.u_id, u.name;
```

-------------------------1786 sample_num
```sql
SELECT A.custid, A.name
FROM ACCOUNTS A
WHERE A.custid IN (SELECT C.custid
                    FROM CHECKING C
                    WHERE C.balance = (SELECT MAX(B.balance)
                                       FROM CHECKING B))
EXCEPT
SELECT S.custid
FROM SAVINGS S;
```
-------------------------1787 sample_num
```sql
SELECT A.custid, A.name
FROM ACCOUNTS A
WHERE A.custid IN (
  SELECT C.custid
  FROM CHECKING C
  WHERE C.balance = (
    SELECT MAX(B.balance)
    FROM CHECKING B
  )
)
AND NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM CHECKING D
  WHERE D.custid = A.custid AND D.balance < (
    SELECT MAX(B.balance)
    FROM CHECKING B
  )
);
```

  )

FROM ACCOUNTS a

  FROM CHECKING c
)

LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------1812 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    SUM(C.balance) AS total_checking_balance,
    SUM(S.balance) AS total_saving_balance,
    (SUM(C.balance) + SUM(S.balance)) AS total_balance
FROM
    CHECKING C
JOIN
    SAVINGS S ON C.custid = S.custid
GROUP BY
    C.custid
ORDER BY
    total_balance ASC;
```

-------------------------1831 sample_num
```sql
SELECT wca.name, wca.Operating_system
FROM Web_client_accelerator wca
WHERE wca.id NOT IN (
  SELECT wca.id
  FROM Web_client_accelerator wca
  JOIN accelerator_compatible_browser acb ON wca.id = acb.accelerator_id
  JOIN browser b ON acb.browser_id = b.id
  JOIN browser_web_connection bwcon ON b.id = bwcon.browser_id
  WHERE bwcon.Connection = 'Broadband'
  GROUP BY wca.id
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT bwcon.Connection) = 1
)
```
-------------------------1832 sample_num
```sql
SELECT b.name
FROM accelerator_compatible_browser acb
JOIN browser b ON acb.browser_id = b.id
WHERE acb.accelerator_id = (SELECT id FROM Web_client_accelerator WHERE name = 'CProxy') AND acb.compatible_since_year > 1998;
```
-------------------------1833 sample_num
```sql
SELECT wa.id, wa.name
FROM Web_client_accelerator wa
WHERE wa.id IN (
  SELECT accelerator_id
  FROM accelerator_compatible_browser
  GROUP BY accelerator_id
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT browser_id) >= 2
)
```
-------------------------1834 sample_num
```sql
SELECT b.id, b.name
FROM browser b
JOIN (
  SELECT browser_id, COUNT(*) as count
  FROM accelerator_compatible_browser
  GROUP BY browser_id
  ORDER BY count DESC
  LIMIT 1
) as c ON b.id = c.browser_id;
```
-------------------------1835 sample_num

JOIN browser ON accelerator_compatible_browser.browser_id = browser.id
WHERE Web_client_accelerator.name = 'CACHEbox' AND browser.name = 'Internet Explorer';

-------------------------1839 sample_num
```sql
SELECT b.name
FROM browser b
JOIN accelerator_compatible_browser abc ON b.id = abc.browser_id
WHERE abc.accelerator_id IN (
  SELECT wa.id
  FROM Web_client_accelerator wa
  WHERE wa.name IN ('CACHEbox', 'Fasterfox')
)
GROUP BY b.name
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT abc.accelerator_id) = 2;
```
-------------------------1840 sample_num
```sql
SELECT wa.name, wa.Operating_system
FROM Web_client_accelerator wa
JOIN accelerator_compatible_browser abc ON wa.id = abc.accelerator_id
WHERE abc.browser_id NOT IN (
    SELECT id
    FROM browser
    WHERE name = 'Opera'
)

FROM accelerator_compatible_browser acb
JOIN browser b ON acb.browser_id = b.id
JOIN Web_client_accelerator wca ON acb.accelerator_id = wca.id
ORDER BY acb.compatible_since_year DESC;

FROM company
ORDER BY Sales_billion DESC;

-------------------------2002 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    Company,
    MIN(Market_Value) AS Min_Market_Value,
    MAX(Market_Value) AS Max_Market_Value,
    AVG(Market_Value) AS Avg_Market_Value
FROM
    gas_company.company
GROUP BY
    Company;
```

-------------------------2009 sample_num
```sql

    Main_Industry,
    SUM(Market_Value) AS Total_Market_Value,
    COUNT(*) AS Number_of_Companies

    Main_Industry

    Total_Market_Value DESC
LIMIT 1;

    Main_Industry;

-------------------------2023 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.Company, COUNT(s.Station_ID) AS Number_of_Stations
FROM company c
JOIN station_company sc ON c.Company_ID = sc.Company_ID
JOIN gas_station s ON sc.Station_ID = s.Station_ID
GROUP BY c.Company;
```
-------------------------2024 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    s.Company,
    COUNT(g.Station_ID) AS Num_Gas_Stations
FROM
    station_company sc
JOIN
    gas_station g ON sc.Station_ID = g.Station_ID
JOIN
    company s ON sc.Company_ID = s.Company_ID
GROUP BY
    s.Company;
```

  FROM company
  ORDER BY Assets_billion DESC
  LIMIT 3
)

-------------------------2081 sample_num
```sql
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM party_events
WHERE Event_Name = 'Annual Meeting'
AND EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM region
  WHERE region.Region_name = 'United Kingdom'
  AND party_events.Party_ID = party.Region_ID
);
```
-------------------------2082 sample_num
```sql
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM party_events
JOIN party ON party_events.Party_ID = party.Party_ID
JOIN member ON party.Member_ID = member.Member_ID
JOIN region ON party.Region_ID = region.Region_ID
WHERE region.Region_name = 'United Kingdom'
AND party_events.Event_Name = 'Annual Meeting';
```

-------------------------2088 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.Join_Year
FROM pilot p
JOIN pilot_record pr ON p.Pilot_ID = pr.Pilot_ID
JOIN (
  SELECT MAX(Rank) as Max_Rank, Pilot_ID
  FROM pilot
  GROUP BY Pilot_ID
) mr ON p.Pilot_ID = mr.Pilot_ID AND p.Rank = mr.Max_Rank;
```

-------------------------2117 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    sa.shipping_agent_name,
    COUNT(d.document_id) AS total_documents
FROM
    Documents d
JOIN
    Ref_Shipping_Agents sa ON d.shipping_agent_code = sa.shipping_agent_code
GROUP BY
    sa.shipping_agent_name
ORDER BY
    total_documents DESC
LIMIT 1;

-------------------------2121 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.document_id
FROM Documents d
JOIN Ref_Document_Status ds ON d.document_status_code = ds.document_status_code
JOIN Ref_Document_Types dt ON d.document_type_code = dt.document_type_code
JOIN Ref_Shipping_Agents sa ON d.shipping_agent_code = sa.shipping_agent_code
WHERE ds.document_status_description = 'Done'
AND dt.document_type_description = 'Paper'
AND sa.shipping_agent_name <> 'USPS';
```
-------------------------2122 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.document_id
FROM Documents d
JOIN Ref_Document_Status rs ON d.document_status_code = rs.document_status_code
JOIN Ref_Document_Types rdt ON d.document_type_code = rdt.document_type_code
JOIN Ref_Shipping_Agents rsa ON d.shipping_agent_code = rsa.shipping_agent_code
WHERE rs.document_status_description = 'Done'
AND rdt.document_type_description = 'Paper'
AND rsa.shipping_agent_name = 'USPS';
```

-------------------------2125 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.document_id, COUNT(*) as num_draft_copies
FROM Draft_Copies dc
JOIN Documents d ON dc.document_id = d.document_id
GROUP BY d.document_id
ORDER BY num_draft_copies DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------2126 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.document_id, COUNT(dc.copy_number) as num_draft_copies
FROM Documents d
JOIN Document_Drafts dd ON d.document_id = dd.document_id
JOIN Draft_Copies dc ON dd.document_id = dc.document_id AND dd.draft_number = dc.draft_number
GROUP BY d.document_id
HAVING COUNT(dc.copy_number) > 1;
```

-------------------------2129 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    e.employee_name,
    COUNT(c.document_id) AS total_drafts_and_copies
FROM
    Circulation_History c
JOIN
    Employees e ON c.employee_id = e.employee_id
GROUP BY
    e.employee_name
ORDER BY
    total_drafts_and_copies DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------2130 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.document_id, COUNT(e.employee_id) AS num_employees
FROM Circulation_History ch
JOIN Documents d ON ch.document_id = d.document_id
JOIN Employees e ON ch.employee_id = e.employee_id
GROUP BY d.document_id;
```

-------------------------2150 sample_num

FROM Services s
WHERE EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM Events e
  WHERE e.Service_ID = s.Service_ID
  AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM Events ef
    WHERE ef.Service_ID = s.Service_ID
    AND ef.Event_Details LIKE '%Failure%'
  )
  AND EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM Events es
    WHERE es.Service_ID = s.Service_ID
    AND es.Event_Details LIKE '%Successful%'
  )
);

-------------------------2169 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.driverId, d.forename, d.surname
FROM drivers d
JOIN lapTimes lt ON d.driverId = lt.driverId
JOIN (
  SELECT raceId, driverId
  FROM lapTimes
  GROUP BY raceId, driverId
  HAVING COUNT(*) >= 2
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) ASC, driverId ASC
  LIMIT 1
) AS twice_fastest ON lt.raceId = twice_fastest.raceId AND lt.driverId = twice_fastest.driverId
ORDER BY lt.raceId, lt.lap ASC;
```

FROM pitStops p1
WHERE p1.raceId = 841
AND NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM pitStops p2
  WHERE p2.raceId = 841
  AND p2.driverId != p1.driverId
  AND p2.stop < p1.stop
)

  UNION

  GROUP BY p.driverId
  HAVING COUNT(p.raceId) > 8
);

  FROM results rs
  GROUP BY rs.driverId
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 5
);

-------------------------2223 sample_num
```sql
SELECT r.name, r.year, MAX(fl.fastestLapSpeed) AS max_fastest_lap_speed
FROM races r
JOIN results res ON r.raceId = res.raceId
JOIN lapTimes lt ON r.raceId = lt.raceId AND res.driverId = lt.driverId
JOIN (
  SELECT raceId, MAX(milliseconds) AS fastestLapTime, (0.621371 * SQRT(2 * 6371 / (lat2 - lat1) + (lng2 - lng1) ** 2)) AS fastestLapSpeed
  FROM lapTimes
  JOIN circuits c ON lapTimes.raceId = c.circuitId
  GROUP BY raceId
) fl ON r.raceId = fl.raceId
WHERE r.year > 2004
GROUP BY r.name, r.year
ORDER BY r.year;
```
-------------------------2224 sample_num
```sql
SELECT r.name, MAX(fl.fastestLapSpeed)
FROM races r
JOIN results res ON r.raceId = res.raceId
JOIN lapTimes fl ON res.raceId = fl.raceId AND res.driverId = fl.driverId
WHERE r.year > 2004
GROUP BY r.name
ORDER BY r.year;
```
-------------------------2225 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    r.name,
    r.year,
    AVG(fastestLapSpeed) AS average_fastest_lap_speed
FROM
    results r
JOIN
    qualifying q ON r.raceId = q.raceId
JOIN
    drivers d ON r.driverId = d.driverId
JOIN
    lapTimes lt ON r.raceId = lt.raceId AND r.driverId = lt.driverId
WHERE
    r.year > 2004
GROUP BY
    r.name, r.year
ORDER BY
    r.year;
```
-------------------------2226 sample_num
```sql

    r.year,
    AVG(fastestLapSpeed) AS avg_fastest_lap_speed
FROM
    results r
JOIN
    lapTimes lt ON r.raceId = lt.raceId
WHERE
    r.year > 2004
GROUP BY
    r.year
ORDER BY
    r.year;
```

-------------------------2360 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.Campus
FROM Campuses c
JOIN faculty f ON c.Id = f.Campus
WHERE c.County = 'Orange' AND f.Year = 2002
EXCEPT
SELECT c.Campus
FROM Campuses c
JOIN faculty f ON c.Id = f.Campus
WHERE f.Year = 2002
GROUP BY c.Campus
HAVING COUNT(f.Campus) > (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM faculty WHERE Year = 2002 AND Campus = c.Campus);
```
-------------------------2361 sample_num
```sql
SELECT Campus
FROM faculty f
JOIN Campuses c ON f.Campus = c.Id
WHERE f.Year = 2002 AND c.County = 'Orange'
AND f.Campus IN (
  SELECT f2.Campus
  FROM faculty f2
  JOIN Campuses c2 ON f2.Campus = c2.Id
  WHERE f2.Year = 2002 AND c2.County = 'Orange'
  GROUP BY f2.Campus
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
  LIMIT 1
)
```

-------------------------2416 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.Name
FROM candidate c
JOIN people p ON c.People_ID = p.People_ID
JOIN (
  SELECT People_ID, Sex, MIN(Oppose_rate) AS Min_Oppose_rate
  FROM candidate
  GROUP BY People_ID, Sex
) m ON c.People_ID = m.People_ID AND c.Oppose_rate = m.Min_Oppose_rate
```
-------------------------2417 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.Sex, p.Name
FROM people p
JOIN candidate c ON p.People_ID = c.People_ID
WHERE c.Oppose_rate = (SELECT MAX(Oppose_rate) FROM candidate WHERE Sex = p.Sex)
```

FROM
    candidate c
JOIN
    people p ON c.People_ID = p.People_ID
GROUP BY
    p.Sex
ORDER BY
    Average_Uncertain_Ratio DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------2470 sample_num
```sql
SELECT M.title, M.director
FROM Movie M
WHERE M.mID IN (
  SELECT R.mID
  FROM Rating R
  WHERE R.rID IN (
    SELECT R2.rID
    FROM Rating R2
    JOIN Movie M2 ON R2.mID = M2.mID
    WHERE M2.director = 'James Cameron'
  )
  AND R.stars > (
    SELECT AVG(R3.stars)
    FROM Rating R3
    JOIN Movie M3 ON R3.mID = M3.mID
    WHERE M3.director = 'James Cameron'
  )
)
```
-------------------------2471 sample_num

FROM Movie M
WHERE M.mID IN (
  SELECT R.mID
  FROM Rating R
  WHERE R.stars > (
    SELECT AVG(R.stars)
    FROM Rating R2
    WHERE R2.mID IN (
      SELECT R3.mID
      FROM Rating R3
      WHERE R3.rID IN (
        SELECT R4.rID
        FROM Reviewer R4
        WHERE R4.name = 'James Cameron'
      )
    )
  )
)

-------------------------2502 sample_num
```sql
SELECT M.director, M.title, R.stars
FROM Movie M
JOIN Rating R ON M.mID = R.mID
JOIN (
  SELECT director, MAX(stars) AS max_stars
  FROM Movie
  JOIN Rating R ON Movie.mID = R.mID
  GROUP BY director
) AS T ON M.director = T.director AND R.stars = T.max_stars
```

-------------------------2505 sample_num
```sql
SELECT R.name, M.title, R.rID, R.mID, R.stars
FROM Rating R
JOIN Movie M ON R.mID = M.mID
JOIN (SELECT rID, mID, MIN(stars) as min_stars
      FROM Rating
      GROUP BY rID, mID) as min_stars_R
ON R.rID = min_stars_R.rID AND R.mID = min_stars_R.mID AND R.stars = min_stars_R.min_stars;
```
-------------------------2506 sample_num
```sql
SELECT M.title, AVG(R.stars) AS score
FROM Movie M
JOIN Rating R ON M.mID = R.mID
JOIN Reviewer RV ON R.rID = RV.rID
WHERE M.director IN (
  SELECT director
  FROM Movie
  GROUP BY director
)
GROUP BY M.title
ORDER BY score ASC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------2507 sample_num
```sql
SELECT M.title, R.stars
FROM Movie M
JOIN Rating R ON M.mID = R.mID
JOIN (
  SELECT mID, MIN(stars) AS min_stars
  FROM Rating
  GROUP BY mID
) MR ON M.mID = MR.mID AND R.stars = MR.min_stars
JOIN MovieDirector MD ON M.mID = MD.mID
GROUP BY M.title, R.stars
```

-------------------------2544 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    ROUND(AVG(CAST(Hispanic AS float)/ (White + Black + Amerindian + Asian + Multiracial + Hispanic) * 100), 2) AS Hispanic_percentage
FROM
    city
WHERE
    Black / (White + Black + Amerindian + Asian + Multiracial) * 100 > 10
GROUP BY
    County_ID
```
-------------------------2545 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    c.Name,
    (c.Hispanic / (c.White + c.Black + c.Amerindian + c.Asian + c.Multiracial + c.Hispanic)) * 100 AS Hispanic_Percentage
FROM
    city c
WHERE
    c.County_ID IN (SELECT County_ID FROM county_public_safety)
    AND c.Black / (c.White + c.Black + c.Amerindian + c.Asian + c.Multiracial) * 100 > 10;
```

  SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id

  SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id
  FROM Benefits_Overpayments

FROM CMI_Cross_References

  FROM Council_Tax

    SELECT council_tax_id
    FROM Parking_Fines
  )
  UNION ALL
  SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id
  FROM Business_Rates
  WHERE business_rates_id IN (
    SELECT council_tax_id
    FROM Parking_Fines
  )
  UNION ALL
  SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id
  FROM Benefits_Overpayments
  WHERE council_tax_id IN (
    SELECT council_tax_id
    FROM Parking_Fines
  )
  UNION ALL
  SELECT cmi_cross_ref_id
  FROM Rent_Arrears
  WHERE council_tax_id IN (
    SELECT council_tax_id
    FROM Parking_Fines
  )
);

LIMIT 1;

-------------------------2857 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    state_province_county AS state_name,
    COUNT(*) AS num_customers
FROM
    Addresses
JOIN
    Customer_Addresses ON Addresses.address_id = Customer_Addresses.address_id
JOIN
    Customers ON Customer_Addresses.customer_id = Customers.customer_id
GROUP BY
    state_province_county
ORDER BY
    num_customers DESC;

-------------------------2938 sample_num

SELECT f.title, f.film_id
FROM film f
JOIN inventory i ON f.film_id = i.film_id
JOIN rental r ON i.inventory_id = r.inventory_id
WHERE f.rental_rate = 0.99 AND i.inventory_id IN (
  SELECT i.film_id
  FROM inventory i
  GROUP BY i.film_id
  HAVING COUNT(i.inventory_id) < 3
);
```

    FROM inventory
    GROUP BY film_id
    HAVING COUNT(*) >= 3
  )
);

-------------------------2951 sample_num

FROM film f
JOIN film_actor fa ON f.film_id = fa.film_id
JOIN film_text ft ON f.film_id = ft.film_id
GROUP BY f.title, f.film_id, ft.description
ORDER BY COUNT(fa.actor_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------2952 sample_num
```sql
SELECT a.first_name, a.last_name, a.actor_id
FROM film_actor fa
JOIN actor a ON fa.actor_id = a.actor_id
GROUP BY fa.actor_id, a.first_name, a.last_name
ORDER BY COUNT(fa.film_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------3068 sample_num
```sql
SELECT bname
FROM bank
WHERE branch_ID IN (
    SELECT branch_ID
    FROM loan
    WHERE cust_ID IN (
        SELECT cust_ID
        FROM customer
        WHERE credit_score < 100
    )
)
ORDER BY (
    SELECT SUM(amount)
    FROM loan
    WHERE branch_ID = bank.branch_ID
    AND cust_ID IN (
        SELECT cust_ID
        FROM customer
        WHERE credit_score < 100
    )
) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

    WHERE credit_score < 100
  )
  GROUP BY branch_ID
) l ON b.branch_ID = l.branch_ID
ORDER BY l.total_amount DESC
LIMIT 1;

-------------------------3128 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    tpc.company_id,
    COUNT(a.asset_id) AS asset_count
FROM
    Assets a
JOIN
    Assets a1 ON a.asset_id = a1.asset_id
JOIN
    Maintenance_Contracts mc ON a.maintenance_contract_id = mc.maintenance_contract_id
JOIN
    Third_Party_Companies tpc ON mc.maintenance_contract_company_id = tpc.company_id
GROUP BY
    tpc.company_id
ORDER BY
    tpc.company_id;

-------------------------3129 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
  c.company_id,
  c.company_name
FROM
  Third_Party_Companies c
WHERE
  c.company_id IN (
    SELECT
      mce.company_id
    FROM
      Maintenance_Engineers me
    JOIN
      Maintenance_Contracts mce ON me.company_id = mce.maintenance_contract_company_id
    GROUP BY
      mce.company_id
    HAVING
      COUNT(me.engineer_id) >= 2
  )
UNION
SELECT
  mc.maintenance_contract_company_id,
  c.company_name
FROM
  Maintenance_Contracts mc
JOIN
  Third_Party_Companies c ON mc.maintenance_contract_company_id = c.company_id
GROUP BY
  mc.maintenance_contract_company_id,
  c.company_name
HAVING
  COUNT(mc.maintenance_contract_id) >= 2;
```

GROUP BY D.DEPT_NAME;

JOIN COURSE Crs ON C.CRS_CODE = Crs.CRS_CODE
WHERE P.EMP_NUM IS NOT NULL;
```

-------------------------3394 sample_num
```sql
SELECT f.Name
FROM furniture f
WHERE f.Furniture_ID IN (
  SELECT fm.Furniture_ID
  FROM furniture_manufacte fm
  WHERE fm.Price_in_Dollar = (
    SELECT MAX(fm.Price_in_Dollar)
    FROM furniture_manufacte fm
  )
) AND NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM furniture_manufacte fm
  WHERE fm.Furniture_ID = f.Furniture_ID AND fm.Price_in_Dollar > (
    SELECT MAX(fm.Price_in_Dollar)
    FROM furniture_manufacte fm
  )
);
```

-------------------------3400 sample_num
```sql
SELECT m.Manufacturer_ID, m.Num_of_Shops
FROM manufacturer m
JOIN furniture_manufacte fm ON m.Manufacturer_ID = fm.Manufacturer_ID
JOIN furniture f ON fm.Furniture_ID = f.Furniture_ID
WHERE (m.Manufacturer_ID, f.Furniture_ID) IN (
    SELECT fm2.Manufacturer_ID, fm2.Furniture_ID
    FROM furniture_manufacte fm2
    WHERE fm2.Price_in_Dollar = (
        SELECT MAX(fm3.Price_in_Dollar)
        FROM furniture_manufacte fm3
    )
)
```
-------------------------3401 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
  m.Name,
  COUNT(f.Furniture_ID) AS Num_of_Furniture
FROM
  manufacturer m
  JOIN furniture_manufacte fm ON m.Manufacturer_ID = fm.Manufacturer_ID
  JOIN furniture f ON fm.Furniture_ID = f.Furniture_ID
GROUP BY
  m.Name;

-------------------------3403 sample_num
```sql
SELECT f.Name, (f.Market_Rate / (SELECT SUM(fm.Price_in_Dollar) FROM furniture_manufacte)) AS Market_Share
FROM furniture f
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM furniture_manufacte fm
  WHERE fm.Furniture_ID = f.Furniture_ID
)
```
-------------------------3404 sample_num
```sql
SELECT m.Name
FROM manufacturer m
JOIN furniture_manufacte fm ON m.Manufacturer_ID = fm.Manufacturer_ID
JOIN furniture f ON fm.Furniture_ID = f.Furniture_ID
WHERE f.Num_of_Component < 6
OR f.Num_of_Component > 10
GROUP BY m.Name
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT f.Furniture_ID) > 1;
```

SELECT e.SALARY, e.MANAGER_ID
FROM employees e
WHERE e.MANAGER_ID IS NOT NULL;
```

FROM employees

FROM employees e
WHERE e.HIRE_DATE < '2002-06-21';

-------------------------3443 sample_num
```sql
SELECT j.JOB_TITLE, j.MAX_SALARY - j.MIN_SALARY AS SALARY_RANGE
FROM jobs j
WHERE j.MAX_SALARY BETWEEN 12000 AND 18000;
```
-------------------------3444 sample_num
```sql
SELECT j.JOB_TITLE, MIN(j.MIN_SALARY) AS MIN_SALARY, MAX(j.MAX_SALARY) AS MAX_SALARY
FROM jobs j
WHERE j.MAX_SALARY BETWEEN 12000 AND 18000
GROUP BY j.JOB_TITLE;
```

-------------------------3447 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.EMPLOYEE_ID, j.END_DATE
FROM employees e
JOIN job_history j ON e.EMPLOYEE_ID = j.EMPLOYEE_ID
WHERE j.END_DATE IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY e.EMPLOYEE_ID;
```
-------------------------3448 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.EMPLOYEE_ID, MAX(jh.END_DATE) AS END_DATE
FROM employees e
JOIN job_history jh ON e.EMPLOYEE_ID = jh.EMPLOYEE_ID
GROUP BY e.EMPLOYEE_ID;
```
-------------------------3449 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.*
FROM departments d
WHERE d.DEPARTMENT_ID IN (
  SELECT e.DEPARTMENT_ID
  FROM employees e
  WHERE e.COMMISSION_PCT IS NOT NULL
  GROUP BY e.DEPARTMENT_ID
  HAVING COUNT(e.EMPLOYEE_ID) > 10
);
```
-------------------------3450 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DEPARTMENT_ID
FROM employees
GROUP BY DEPARTMENT_ID
HAVING COUNT(CASE WHEN COMMISSION_PCT IS NOT NULL THEN 1 END) > 10;
```
-------------------------3451 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.DEPARTMENT_ID
FROM departments d
WHERE d.DEPARTMENT_ID IN (
  SELECT e.DEPARTMENT_ID
  FROM employees e
  GROUP BY e.DEPARTMENT_ID
  HAVING COUNT(e.MANAGER_ID) >= 4
)
```
-------------------------3452 sample_num
```sql

FROM employees
WHERE MANAGER_ID IN (
  SELECT EMPLOYEE_ID
  FROM employees
  GROUP BY EMPLOYEE_ID
  HAVING COUNT(EMPLOYEE_ID) > 3
)
```
-------------------------3453 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    d.DEPARTMENT_NAME,
    AVG(e.SALARY) AS AVG_SALARY
FROM
    employees e
JOIN
    departments d ON e.DEPARTMENT_ID = d.DEPARTMENT_ID
WHERE
    e.COMMISSION_PCT IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY
    d.DEPARTMENT_NAME;
```

-------------------------3457 sample_num
```sql
SELECT JOB_ID
FROM employees e
JOIN job_history j ON e.EMPLOYEE_ID = j.EMPLOYEE_ID
GROUP BY JOB_ID
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT e.EMPLOYEE_ID) >= 2 AND SUM(DATEDIFF(j.END_DATE, j.START_DATE)) > 300;
```
-------------------------3458 sample_num
```sql
SELECT j.JOB_ID
FROM jobs j
JOIN job_history jh ON j.JOB_ID = jh.JOB_ID
GROUP BY j.JOB_ID
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT jh.END_DATE - jh.START_DATE) > 1 AND MAX(jh.END_DATE - jh.START_DATE) > 300;
```

-------------------------3465 sample_num
```sql
SELECT j.*
FROM jobs j
WHERE j.JOB_ID IN (
  SELECT jh.JOB_ID
  FROM job_history jh
  WHERE jh.END_DATE IS NULL
  AND jh.EMPLOYEE_ID IN (
    SELECT e.EMPLOYEE_ID
    FROM employees e
    WHERE e.SALARY >= 12000
  )
)
```
-------------------------3466 sample_num

FROM job_history jh

WHERE e.SALARY >= 12000;

-------------------------3472 sample_num

-------------------------3473 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.FIRST_NAME, e.LAST_NAME, d.DEPARTMENT_ID
FROM employees e
JOIN departments d ON e.DEPARTMENT_ID = d.DEPARTMENT_ID
WHERE e.SALARY = (SELECT MIN(salary) FROM (SELECT DEPARTMENT_ID, AVG(SALARY) AS salary FROM employees GROUP BY DEPARTMENT_ID) AS avg_salary);
```
-------------------------3474 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.FIRST_NAME, e.LAST_NAME, d.DEPARTMENT_ID
FROM employees e
JOIN jobs j ON e.JOB_ID = j.JOB_ID
JOIN departments d ON e.DEPARTMENT_ID = d.DEPARTMENT_ID
WHERE e.SALARY = (SELECT MIN(salary) FROM employees);
```

-------------------------3503 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.EMPLOYEE_ID, e.FIRST_NAME, e.LAST_NAME
FROM employees e
WHERE e.DEPARTMENT_ID IN (
  SELECT d.DEPARTMENT_ID
  FROM departments d
  WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM employees
    WHERE JOB_ID IN (
      SELECT j.JOB_ID
      FROM jobs j
      WHERE JOB_TITLE LIKE '%T%'
    ) AND DEPARTMENT_ID = d.DEPARTMENT_ID
  )
);
```
-------------------------3504 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.EMPLOYEE_ID, e.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || e.LAST_NAME AS FULL_NAME
FROM employees e
WHERE e.DEPARTMENT_ID IN (
  SELECT d.DEPARTMENT_ID
  FROM departments d
  WHERE d.DEPARTMENT_ID IN (
    SELECT jh.DEPARTMENT_ID
    FROM job_history jh
    WHERE jh.EMPLOYEE_ID IN (
      SELECT e.EMPLOYEE_ID
      FROM employees e
      WHERE e.FIRST_NAME LIKE '%T%'
    )
  )
)
```
-------------------------3505 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.EMPLOYEE_ID, e.FIRST_NAME, e.LAST_NAME, e.SALARY
FROM employees e
WHERE e.SALARY > (SELECT AVG(SALARY) FROM employees)
AND e.DEPARTMENT_ID IN (
  SELECT d.DEPARTMENT_ID
  FROM departments d
  WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM employees
    WHERE JOB_ID = 'J%' AND DEPARTMENT_ID = d.DEPARTMENT_ID
  )
);
```
-------------------------3506 sample_num
```sql
SELECT e.EMPLOYEE_ID, e.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || e.LAST_NAME AS FULL_NAME, e.SALARY
FROM employees e
WHERE e.SALARY > (SELECT AVG(SALARY) FROM employees)
AND e.DEPARTMENT_ID IN (
  SELECT d.DEPARTMENT_ID
  FROM departments d
  WHERE d.DEPARTMENT_ID IN (
    SELECT jh.DEPARTMENT_ID
    FROM job_history jh
    WHERE EXISTS (
      SELECT 1
      FROM employees em
      WHERE em.FIRST_NAME LIKE '%J%' AND em.DEPARTMENT_ID = jh.DEPARTMENT_ID
    )
  )
);
```

-------------------------3515 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    d.DEPARTMENT_ID,
    e.FIRST_NAME || ' ' || e.LAST_NAME AS FULL_NAME,
    e.SALARY
FROM
    employees e
JOIN
    departments d ON e.DEPARTMENT_ID = d.DEPARTMENT_ID
WHERE
    (e.SALARY, e.DEPARTMENT_ID) IN (
        SELECT
            MAX(SALARY),
            DEPARTMENT_ID
        FROM
            employees
        GROUP BY
            DEPARTMENT_ID
    );
```
-------------------------3516 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.DEPARTMENT_ID, CONCAT(e.FIRST_NAME, ' ', e.LAST_NAME) AS FULL_NAME, e.SALARY
FROM employees e
JOIN departments d ON e.DEPARTMENT_ID = d.DEPARTMENT_ID
WHERE e.SALARY = (SELECT MAX(e2.SALARY) FROM employees e2 WHERE e2.DEPARTMENT_ID = e.DEPARTMENT_ID)
```

FROM employees e
JOIN locations l ON e.LOCATION_ID = l.LOCATION_ID
JOIN departments d ON e.DEPARTMENT_ID = d.LOCATION_ID
WHERE l.CITY = 'London';
```

    g_name,
    MIN(duration) AS shortest_duration,

-------------------------3604 sample_num
```sql
SELECT g_name, song_name, rating
FROM (
  SELECT g_name, song_name, rating, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY g_name ORDER BY duration, rating) AS rn
  FROM song
  JOIN files ON song.f_id = files.f_id
  JOIN artist ON song.artist_name = artist.artist_name
  JOIN genre ON song.genre_is = genre.g_name
  WHERE rating IS NOT NULL
) AS subquery
WHERE rn = 1
ORDER BY g_name, rating;
```

-------------------------3643 sample_num
```sql
SELECT m.player_id, m.name_first, m.name_last
FROM manager m
JOIN manager_award ma ON m.player_id = ma.player_id
JOIN (SELECT player_id, COUNT(*) as award_count
      FROM manager_award
      GROUP BY player_id
      ORDER BY award_count DESC
      LIMIT 1) as top_award ON m.player_id = top_award.player_id;
```

ORDER BY COUNT(ma.award_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;

SELECT t.name, t.team_id, MAX(s.salary) AS max_salary
FROM salary s
JOIN team t ON s.team_id = t.team_id
GROUP BY t.name, t.team_id;
```
-------------------------3658 sample_num

-------------------------3659 sample_num
```sql

FROM team t
JOIN salary s ON t.team_id = s.team_id
ORDER BY AVG(s.salary) ASC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------3660 sample_num
```sql
SELECT t.name, t.team_id
FROM team t
JOIN salary s ON t.team_id = s.team_id
JOIN (
  SELECT team_id, AVG(salary) AS avg_salary
  FROM salary
  GROUP BY team_id
) AS avg_salary_table ON t.team_id = avg_salary_table.team_id
ORDER BY avg_salary_table.avg_salary ASC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------3661 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.name_first, p.name_last
FROM player p
JOIN player_award pa ON p.player_id = pa.player_id
WHERE pa.year IN (1960, 1961)
GROUP BY p.name_first, p.name_last
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT pa.year) = 2;
```
-------------------------3662 sample_num

JOIN manager_award ma ON p.player_id = ma.player_id
JOIN manager_award ma1 ON p.player_id = ma1.player_id
WHERE ma.year = 1960 AND ma1.year = 1961;

FROM postseason p
JOIN team t ON p.team_id_winner = t.team_id AND p.year = t.year
JOIN team t2 ON p.team_id_loser = t2.team_id AND p.year = t2.year
WHERE t.name = 'Boston Red Stockings' AND p.year = 2009 AND p.round = 'postseason';

  cl.name

  num_mountains DESC;

-------------------------3806 sample_num
```sql

FROM Course_Authors_and_Tutors ca
JOIN Courses c ON ca.author_id = c.author_id
GROUP BY ca.author_id, ca.personal_name, ca.family_name
ORDER BY COUNT(c.course_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------3807 sample_num
```sql
SELECT caa.author_id, caa.personal_name, caa.family_name
FROM Course_Authors_and_Tutors caa
JOIN (
  SELECT author_id, COUNT(*) as course_count
  FROM Courses
  GROUP BY author_id
  ORDER BY course_count DESC
  LIMIT 1
) as max_courses
ON caa.author_id = max_courses.author_id;
```

HAVING COUNT(c.course_id) >= 2;

-------------------------3850 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.Date_Claim_Made, c.Claim_ID
FROM Claims c
WHERE c.Claim_ID IN (
    SELECT s.Claim_ID
    FROM Settlements s
    GROUP BY s.Claim_ID
    HAVING COUNT(s.Settlement_ID) > 2
    UNION
    SELECT c.Claim_ID
    FROM Claims c
    WHERE c.Amount_Claimed = (
        SELECT MAX(c2.Amount_Claimed)
        FROM Claims c2
    )
)
```

-------------------------3856 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    s.Amount_Settled AS Settlement_Amount,
    c.Amount_Claimed AS Claim_Amount
FROM
    Settlements s
JOIN
    Claims c ON s.Claim_ID = c.Claim_ID
ORDER BY
    c.Amount_Claimed DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------3857 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
  c.Amount_Claimed AS Claim_Amount,
  s.Amount_Settled AS Settlement_Amount
FROM
  Claims c
  INNER JOIN Settlements s ON c.Claim_ID = s.Claim_ID
WHERE
  c.Amount_Claimed = (
    SELECT
      MAX(Amount_Claimed)
    FROM
      Claims
  );
```
-------------------------3858 sample_num

  c.Amount_Claimed AS Claim_Amount
FROM
  Claims c
WHERE
  c.Amount_Settled = (SELECT MIN(Amount_Settled) FROM Claims);
```

FROM Physician p
JOIN Affiliated_With aw ON p.EmployeeID = aw.Physician

ORDER BY NumEmployees DESC
LIMIT 1;

FROM Department d

ON d.DepartmentID = min_employee_count.DepartmentID

FROM teachers t

  SELECT Classroom, COUNT(*) as count
  FROM list
  GROUP BY Classroom
  ORDER BY count DESC
) c ON t.Classroom = c.Classroom
LIMIT 1;
```

LIMIT 1;

-------------------------4232 sample_num
```sql
SELECT RL.Location_Code, RL.Location_Name
FROM Ref_Locations RL
LEFT JOIN (
  SELECT Document_ID, Location_Code
  FROM Document_Locations
  GROUP BY Document_ID, Location_Code
) DL ON RL.Location_Code = DL.Location_Code
GROUP BY RL.Location_Code, RL.Location_Name
ORDER BY COUNT(DL.Document_ID) ASC
LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------4326 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    MIN(date_from) AS start_date,
    MAX(date_to) AS end_date
FROM
    Project_Staff
WHERE
    project_id = (
        SELECT
            project_id
        FROM
            Project_Staff
        GROUP BY
            project_id
        ORDER BY
            COUNT(staff_id) DESC
        LIMIT 1
    );
```
-------------------------4327 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    MIN(date_from) AS start_date,
    MAX(date_to) AS end_date
FROM
    Project_Staff
WHERE
    project_id IN (
        SELECT
            project_id
        FROM
            Project_Staff
        GROUP BY
            project_id
        ORDER BY
            COUNT(*) DESC,
            role_code
        LIMIT 1
    )
AND
    role_code IN (
        SELECT
            role_code
        FROM
            Staff_Roles
        WHERE
            role_description = 'Leader'
    );
```

-------------------------4332 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
  ot.organisation_type,
  COUNT(rs.employer_organisation_id) AS total_research_staff
FROM
  Research_Staff rs
  JOIN Organisations o ON rs.employer_organisation_id = o.organisation_id
  JOIN Organisation_Types ot ON o.organisation_type = ot.organisation_type
GROUP BY
  ot.organisation_type
ORDER BY
  total_research_staff DESC
LIMIT 1;

-------------------------4333 sample_num

GROUP BY ot.organisation_type

LIMIT 1;

-------------------------4466 sample_num

FROM Person P
JOIN PersonFriend PF ON P.name = PF.name

  SELECT name
  FROM Person
  WHERE age > (SELECT AVG(age) FROM Person)
);

-------------------------4514 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.document_name
FROM Documents d
JOIN Document_Structures ds ON d.document_structure_code = ds.document_structure_code
JOIN (
  SELECT document_structure_code
  FROM Document_Structures
  GROUP BY document_structure_code
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
  LIMIT 3
) AS most_common_structures ON ds.document_structure_code IN (most_common_structures.document_structure_code)
JOIN (
  SELECT document_type_code
  FROM Documents
  GROUP BY document_type_code
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
  LIMIT 3
) AS most_common_types ON d.document_type_code IN (most_common_types.document_type_code)
GROUP BY d.document_name
```

  FROM Products p2

  AND p2.Product_Price < 3000
);

-------------------------4593 sample_num

SELECT P.Product_Name, COUNT(PiE.Event_ID) AS Event_Count
FROM Products P
JOIN Products_in_Events PiE ON P.Product_ID = PiE.Product_ID
GROUP BY P.Product_Name;
```
-------------------------4594 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.Product_Name, COUNT(pe.Product_in_Event_ID) AS Event_Count
FROM Products p
JOIN Products_in_Events pe ON p.Product_ID = pe.Product_ID
GROUP BY p.Product_Name
ORDER BY Event_Count DESC;
```
-------------------------4595 sample_num
```sql
SELECT P.Product_Name
FROM Products P
WHERE P.Product_ID IN (
  SELECT PI.Product_ID
  FROM Products_in_Events PI
  GROUP BY PI.Product_ID
  HAVING COUNT(PI.Event_ID) >= 2
);
```
-------------------------4596 sample_num
```sql
SELECT P.Product_Name
FROM Products P
WHERE P.Product_ID IN (
  SELECT PiE.Product_ID
  FROM Products_in_Events PiE
  GROUP BY PiE.Product_ID
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PiE.Event_ID) >= 2
)
ORDER BY P.Product_Name ASC;
```

  SELECT 1
  FROM Products_in_Events pie
  WHERE pie.Product_ID = p.Product_ID
);

-------------------------4630 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.customer_name, c.payment_method
FROM Customers c
JOIN Mailshot_Customers mc1 ON c.customer_id = mc1.customer_id
JOIN Mailshot_Customers mc2 ON c.customer_id = mc2.customer_id
WHERE mc1.mailshot_id IN (
  SELECT mailshot_id
  FROM Mailshot_Customers
  WHERE outcome_code = 'Order'
)
AND mc2.mailshot_id IN (
  SELECT mailshot_id
  FROM Mailshot_Customers
  WHERE outcome_code = 'No Response'
)
```

JOIN Customer_Addresses ca ON c.customer_address = ca.address_id
JOIN Customer_Orders co ON c.customer_id = co.customer_id
WHERE co.order_status_code IN ('New', 'Pending')
GROUP BY c.customer_name, ca.address_details
```

-------------------------4767 sample_num
```sql
SELECT product_id
FROM (
  SELECT product_id, COUNT(*) as order_count
  FROM Order_Items
  GROUP BY product_id
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 3
  UNION ALL
  SELECT product_id, SUM(total_value_purchased) as total_value
  FROM Product_Suppliers
  GROUP BY product_id
  HAVING SUM(total_value_purchased) > 80000
) AS temp
```
-------------------------4768 sample_num
```sql
SELECT product_id
FROM (
  SELECT product_id, COUNT(*) as order_count, SUM(total_amount_purchased) as total_amount
  FROM Order_Items
  JOIN Product_Suppliers ON Order_Items.product_id = Product_Suppliers.product_id
  GROUP BY product_id
) as subquery
WHERE order_count > 3 OR total_amount > 80000;
```

    Residents r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id
ORDER BY
    r.date_moved_in;
```
-------------------------4850 sample_num
```sql
SELECT CE.Customer_Event_ID, CE.property_id
FROM Customer_Events CE
JOIN Customer_Event_Notes CEN ON CE.Customer_Event_ID = CEN.Customer_Event_ID
WHERE CEN.Customer_Event_ID IN (
  SELECT Customer_Event_ID
  FROM (
    SELECT Customer_Event_ID, COUNT(*) as count
    FROM Customer_Event_Notes
    GROUP BY Customer_Event_ID
  ) x
  WHERE count BETWEEN 1 AND 3
)
```

```

```

FROM Player, Tryout
WHERE Tryout.decision = 'yes' AND Player.pID = Tryout.pID;

FROM shop s

) as t ON s.Shop_ID = t.Shop_ID

) AS t ON s.Shop_ID = t.Shop_ID

-------------------------5128 sample_num

    r.service_type_description,
    r.service_type_code,
    COUNT(*) AS service_type_count
FROM
    Ref_Service_Types r
LEFT JOIN
    Services s ON r.service_type_code = s.service_type_code
GROUP BY
    r.service_type_code,
    r.service_type_description
ORDER BY
    service_type_count DESC;

FROM (

  FROM Services
  GROUP BY Service_Type_Code
  ORDER BY count DESC
  LIMIT 1
) r;
```
-------------------------5131 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    s.Service_Type_Code,
    s.Service_Type_Description
FROM
    Services s
JOIN (
    SELECT
        Service_Type_Code,
        COUNT(*) as Total_Performances
    FROM
        Bookings_Services
    GROUP BY
        Service_Type_Code
    ORDER BY
        Total_Performances DESC
    LIMIT 1
) AS max_performances ON s.Service_Type_Code = max_performances.Service_Type_Code
```

  SELECT Order_ID
  FROM Order_Items
  WHERE Order_Quantity * Product_Price > 1000
)
```
-------------------------5147 sample_num

FROM Bookings
WHERE Order_ID IN (
  SELECT Order_ID
  FROM Customer_Orders
  WHERE Order_ID IN (
    SELECT Order_ID
    FROM Order_Items
    WHERE Order_ID IN (
      SELECT Order_ID
      FROM Invoices
      WHERE Order_Quantity * Product_Price > 1000
    )
  )
)

-------------------------5400 sample_num
```sql
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM branch
WHERE Branch_ID IN (
  SELECT Branch_ID
  FROM membership_register_branch
  GROUP BY Branch_ID
  HAVING COUNT(*) > (
    SELECT AVG(COUNT(*))
    FROM membership_register_branch
    GROUP BY Branch_ID
  )
);
```
-------------------------5401 sample_num
```sql
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM branch b
WHERE (SELECT COUNT(*)
       FROM membership_register_branch mr
       WHERE mr.Branch_ID = b.Branch_ID) > (SELECT AVG(COUNT(*))
                                              FROM membership_register_branch
                                              GROUP BY Branch_ID);
```

FROM branch b

ON b.Branch_ID = t.Branch_ID;

SELECT DISTINCT b.Open_year
FROM branch b
GROUP BY b.Open_year
HAVING COUNT(b.Branch_ID) >= 2;
```

-------------------------5420 sample_num

FROM member m

ORDER BY mr.Register_Year;

FROM branch b

WHERE mr.Register_Year > 2015
GROUP BY b.Name;

-------------------------5428 sample_num
```sql
SELECT b.Name, b.Open_year
FROM branch b
JOIN (
  SELECT Branch_ID, COUNT(*) as total_memberships
  FROM membership_register_branch
  WHERE Register_Year = 2016
  GROUP BY Branch_ID
  ORDER BY total_memberships DESC
  LIMIT 1
) t ON b.Branch_ID = t.Branch_ID
```
-------------------------5429 sample_num
```sql
SELECT b.Name, b.Open_year
FROM branch b
JOIN membership_register_branch mr ON b.Branch_ID = mr.Branch_ID
WHERE mr.Register_Year = 2016
GROUP BY b.Name, b.Open_year
ORDER BY COUNT(mr.Member_ID) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------5432 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT b.City
FROM branch b
JOIN membership_register_branch mr ON b.Branch_ID = mr.Branch_ID
WHERE b.Open_year = 2001 AND mr.Branch_ID IN (
  SELECT Branch_ID
  FROM membership_register_branch
  GROUP BY Branch_ID
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 100
)
```
-------------------------5433 sample_num

  FROM membership_register_branch mr

  GROUP BY mr.Branch_ID
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 100
);
```
-------------------------5434 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT b.City
FROM branch b
LEFT JOIN (
  SELECT Branch_ID, COUNT(*) as Total_members
  FROM membership_register_branch
  GROUP BY Branch_ID
) mr ON b.Branch_ID = mr.Branch_ID
WHERE mr.Total_members <= 100 AND mr.Branch_ID IS NULL;
```

  GROUP BY mrb.Branch_ID
  HAVING COUNT(m.Member_ID) > 100
)

-------------------------5530 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
  p.product_name,
  rc.color_description,
  p.product_description
FROM
  Products p
  JOIN Ref_Product_Categories rpc ON p.product_category_code = rpc.product_category_code
  JOIN Ref_Colors rc ON p.color_code = rc.color_code
WHERE
  rpc.product_category_code = (SELECT product_category_code FROM Ref_Product_Categories WHERE product_category_description = 'Herbs');
```

-------------------------5548 sample_num
```sql
SELECT P.product_id, RC.color_description
FROM Products P
JOIN Product_Characteristics PC ON P.product_id = PC.product_id
JOIN Characteristics C ON PC.characteristic_id = C.characteristic_id
JOIN Ref_Colors RC ON P.color_code = RC.color_code
GROUP BY P.product_id, RC.color_description
HAVING COUNT(PC.product_id) >= 2;
```
-------------------------5549 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.product_id, rc.color_description
FROM Products p
JOIN Ref_Colors rc ON p.color_code = rc.color_code
JOIN (
  SELECT product_id
  FROM Product_Characteristics
  GROUP BY product_id
  HAVING COUNT(*) >= 2
) pc ON p.product_id = pc.product_id;
```

-------------------------5595 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.characteristic_name
FROM Characteristics c
JOIN Product_Characteristics pc ON c.characteristic_id = pc.characteristic_id
JOIN (
  SELECT characteristic_id, COUNT(*) as count
  FROM Product_Characteristics
  GROUP BY characteristic_id
) as cnt ON c.characteristic_id = cnt.characteristic_id
ORDER BY cnt.count DESC
LIMIT 1;

-------------------------5618 sample_num
```sql
SELECT r.Result
FROM record r
JOIN swimmer s ON r.Swimmer_ID = s.ID
WHERE s.Nationality = 'Australia'
AND r.ID IN (
  SELECT r.ID
  FROM record r
  WHERE r.Swimmer_ID = s.ID
  AND r.Result LIKE '%meter_200%'
  UNION
  SELECT r.ID
  FROM record r
  WHERE r.Swimmer_ID = s.ID
  AND r.Result LIKE '%meter_300%'
);
```

-------------------------5666 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.customer_name, c.customer_phone
FROM Customers c
JOIN (SELECT customer_id, SUM(order_quantity) AS total_quantity
      FROM Order_Items
      GROUP BY customer_id
      ORDER BY total_quantity DESC
      LIMIT 1) AS most_ordered_customer
ON c.customer_id = most_ordered_customer.customer_id;

-------------------------5702 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.dorm_name
FROM Dorm d
JOIN Has_amenity ha ON d.dormid = ha.dormid
JOIN Dorm_amenity da ON ha.amenid = da.amenid
WHERE da.amenity_name IN ('TV Lounge', 'Study Room')
GROUP BY d.dorm_name
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT da.amenity_name) = 2;
```
-------------------------5703 sample_num
```sql
SELECT D.dorm_name
FROM Dorm D
JOIN Has_amenity HA ON D.dormid = HA.dormid
JOIN Dorm_amenity DA ON HA.amenid = DA.amenid
WHERE DA.amenity_name IN ('TV Lounge', 'Study Room')
GROUP BY D.dorm_name
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT DA.amenity_name) = 2;
```
-------------------------5704 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.dorm_name
FROM Dorm d
JOIN Has_amenity ha ON d.dormid = ha.dormid
JOIN Dorm_amenity da ON ha.amenid = da.amenid
WHERE da.amenity_name = 'TV Lounge'
AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Has_amenity ha2 JOIN Dorm_amenity da2 ON ha2.amenid = da2.amenid WHERE ha2.dormid = d.dormid AND da2.amenity_name = 'Study Room');
```
-------------------------5705 sample_num
```sql
SELECT D.dorm_name
FROM Dorm D
JOIN Has_amenity HA ON D.dormid = HA.dormid
JOIN Dorm_amenity DA ON HA.amenid = DA.amenid
WHERE DA.amenity_name = 'TV Lounge' AND NOT EXISTS
    (SELECT * FROM Dorm_amenity DA2 WHERE DA2.amenity_name = 'study rooms' AND DA2.amenid = HA.amenid);
```

-------------------------5735 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
  d.gender,
  COUNT(*) AS num_students
FROM
  Student s
  JOIN Dorm d ON s.city_code = d.city_code
WHERE
  s.Age > (SELECT AVG(Age) FROM Student WHERE Sex = d.gender)
GROUP BY
  d.gender;
```

-------------------------5774 sample_num
```sql

FROM Products p
JOIN Complaints c ON p.product_id = c.product_id
GROUP BY p.product_name
ORDER BY complaint_count DESC;
```

GROUP BY p.product_name;

-------------------------5776 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.email_address
FROM Customers c

LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------5777 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.email_address
FROM Customers c
JOIN Complaints cm ON c.customer_id = cm.customer_id
WHERE cm.product_id IN (
  SELECT product_id
  FROM Complaints
  GROUP BY product_id
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
  LIMIT 1
);
```
-------------------------5778 sample_num
```sql
SELECT P.product_name
FROM Complaints C
JOIN Products P ON C.product_id = P.product_id
JOIN (
    SELECT customer_id, COUNT(complaint_id) as count
    FROM Complaints
    GROUP BY customer_id
    ORDER BY count ASC
    LIMIT 1
) AS min_complaints ON C.customer_id = min_complaints.customer_id
GROUP BY P.product_name
```
-------------------------5779 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.product_name
FROM Products p
WHERE p.product_id IN (
  SELECT c.product_id
  FROM Complaints c
  GROUP BY c.product_id
  ORDER BY COUNT(c.complaint_id) ASC
  LIMIT 1
)
```

-------------------------5883 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
  t.transaction_id,
  t.date_of_transaction,
  t.amount_of_transaction,
  t.share_count,
  t.other_details,
  CASE
    WHEN t.transaction_type_code IN (SELECT transaction_type_code FROM Ref_Transaction_Types WHERE transaction_type_description = 'Sale') THEN 'Sale'
    WHEN t.transaction_type_code IN (SELECT transaction_type_code FROM Ref_Transaction_Types WHERE transaction_type_description = 'Purchase') THEN 'Purchase'
  END AS transaction_type
FROM
  Transactions t
WHERE
  t.transaction_type_code IN (SELECT transaction_type_code FROM Ref_Transaction_Types WHERE transaction_type_description IN ('Sale', 'Purchase'));
```

);

-------------------------5922 sample_num

FROM Tourist_Attractions ta
JOIN Royal_Family rf ON ta.Tourist_Attraction_ID = rf.Royal_Family_ID
JOIN Locations l ON ta.Location_ID = l.Location_ID
JOIN Ref_Attraction_Types t ON ta.Attraction_Type_Code = t.Attraction_Type_Code
JOIN Theme_Parks tp ON ta.Theme_Park_ID = tp.Theme_Park_ID
JOIN Tourist_Attractions tath ON ta.Tourist_Attraction_ID = tath.Tourist_Attraction_ID
WHERE rf.Royal_Family_ID IS NOT NULL;

  FROM Tourist_Attractions
  WHERE How_to_Get_There LIKE '%walk%' OR How_to_Get_There LIKE '%bus%'
);

-------------------------5946 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    transportation_method,
    COUNT(*) AS frequency
FROM
    (SELECT
        'By Car' AS transportation_method
        FROM
            Visits v
            JOIN Tourist_Attractions ta ON v.Tourist_Attraction_ID = ta.Tourist_Attraction_ID
        WHERE
            How_to_Get_There LIKE '%car%'
    UNION ALL
    SELECT
        'By Public Transport' AS transportation_method
        FROM
            Visits v
            JOIN Tourist_Attractions ta ON v.Tourist_Attraction_ID = ta.Tourist_Attraction_ID
        WHERE
            How_to_Get_There LIKE '%public%'
    UNION ALL
    SELECT
        'On Foot' AS transportation_method
        FROM
            Visits v
            JOIN Tourist_Attractions ta ON v.Tourist_Attraction_ID = ta.Tourist_Attraction_ID
        WHERE
            How_to_Get_There LIKE '%on foot%'
    UNION ALL
    SELECT
        'By Bike' AS transportation_method
        FROM
            Visits v
            JOIN Tourist_Attractions ta ON v.Tourist_Attraction_ID = ta.Tourist_Attraction_ID
        WHERE
            How_to_Get_There LIKE '%bike%'
    UNION ALL
    SELECT
        'By Taxi' AS transportation_method
        FROM
            Visits v
            JOIN Tourist_Attractions ta ON v.Tourist_Attraction_ID = ta.Tourist_Attraction_ID
        WHERE
            How_to_Get_There LIKE '%taxi%'
    UNION ALL
    SELECT
        'Other' AS transportation_method
        FROM
            Visits v
            JOIN Tourist_Attractions ta ON v.Tourist_Attraction_ID = ta.Tourist_Attraction_ID
        WHERE
            How_to_Get_There NOT LIKE '%car%'
            AND How_to_Get_There NOT LIKE '%public%'
            AND How_to_Get_There NOT LIKE '%on foot%'
            AND How_to_Get_There NOT LIKE '%bike%'
            AND How_to_Get_There NOT LIKE '%taxi%'
    ) AS transportation_methods
GROUP BY
    transportation_method
ORDER BY
    frequency DESC;
```
-------------------------5947 sample_num
```sql
SELECT r.attraction_type_description, r.attraction_type_code
FROM (
  SELECT a.attraction_type_code, COUNT(*) as count
  FROM Tourist_Attractions a
  JOIN Ref_Attraction_Types r ON a.attraction_type_code = r.attraction_type_code
  GROUP BY a.attraction_type_code
  ORDER BY count DESC
) r
WHERE r.count = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Tourist_Attractions);
```
-------------------------5948 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    rt.Attraction_Type_Code,
    rt.Attraction_Type_Description
FROM
    Ref_Attraction_Types rt
WHERE
    rt.Attraction_Type_Code = (
        SELECT
            tat.Attraction_Type_Code
        FROM
            Tourist_Attractions tat
        GROUP BY
            tat.Attraction_Type_Code
        ORDER BY
            COUNT(tat.Tourist_Attraction_ID) DESC
        LIMIT 1
    );
```

FROM tourist_attractions t
JOIN visits v ON t.tourist_attraction_id = v.tourist_attraction_id
GROUP BY t.tourist_attraction_id, t.name
HAVING COUNT(v.visit_id) >= 2;

FROM Plays_Games PG
JOIN Video_Games V ON PG.GameID = V.GameID
WHERE PG.StuID IN (SELECT StuID FROM Plays_Games GROUP BY StuID HAVING SUM(Hours_Played) >= 1000);
```
-------------------------6046 sample_num
```sql

FROM Video_Games V
JOIN Plays_Games P ON V.GameID = P.GameID
WHERE P.Hours_Played >= 1000;
```

-------------------------6324 sample_num
```sql
SELECT i.individual_last_name
FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals oci
JOIN Individuals i ON oci.individual_id = i.individual_id
JOIN Organizations o ON oci.organization_id = o.organization_id
WHERE o.uk_vat_number = (
    SELECT MAX(uk_vat_number) FROM Organizations
)
AND oci.date_contact_from = (
    SELECT MIN(date_contact_from) FROM Organization_Contact_Individuals
    WHERE organization_id = o.organization_id
);
```

JOIN Organizations o ON oci.organization_id = o.organization_id
WHERE o.uk_vat_number = (SELECT MAX(uk_vat_number) FROM Organizations)
ORDER BY oci.date_contact_from ASC
LIMIT 1;

FROM Parties P

JOIN (
  SELECT party_id, COUNT(*) as service_count
  FROM Party_Services
  GROUP BY party_id
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
  LIMIT 1
) AS max_services ON P.party_id = max_services.party_id;

WHERE d.Document_Name LIKE '%s%' AND de.Budget_Type_Code IN (SELECT Budget_Type_Code FROM Ref_Budget_Codes);
```
-------------------------6462 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.Document_ID
FROM Documents d
JOIN Documents_with_Expenses de ON d.Document_ID = de.Document_ID
WHERE d.Document_Name LIKE '%s%' AND de.Document_ID IS NOT NULL;
```

-------------------------6512 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.Name
FROM Scientists s
WHERE s.SSN NOT IN (
  SELECT a.Scientist
  FROM AssignedTo a
  JOIN Projects p ON a.Project = p.Code
  JOIN (
    SELECT Code, SUM(Hours) as TotalHours
    FROM Projects
    GROUP BY Code
    ORDER BY TotalHours DESC
    LIMIT 1
  ) t ON p.Code = t.Code
)
```

-------------------------6565 sample_num
```sql
SELECT g.Color
FROM grapes g
JOIN wine w ON g.ID = w.Grape
JOIN (SELECT Grape, AVG(Price) AS AvgPrice
      FROM wine
      GROUP BY Grape
      ORDER BY AvgPrice DESC
      LIMIT 1) AS top_price
ON g.ID = top_price.Grape;
```

FROM station

  FROM station
  WHERE Number_of_Platforms >= 15

  FROM station
  WHERE Total_Passengers > 25
);
```
-------------------------6607 sample_num
```sql

FROM station
WHERE Station_ID NOT IN (
  SELECT Station_ID
  FROM train_station
  JOIN station ON train_station.Station_ID = station.Station_ID
  WHERE Number_of_Platforms >= 15
)
```

FROM train t

JOIN station s ON ts.Station_ID = s.Station_ID
WHERE s.Location = 'London'
ORDER BY t.Time DESC;
```
-------------------------6615 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.Name
FROM station s
JOIN (
  SELECT Station_ID, COUNT(*) as Total_Trains
  FROM train_station
  GROUP BY Station_ID
) t ON s.Station_ID = t.Station_ID
WHERE t.Total_Trains = (
  SELECT MAX(Total_Trains)
  FROM (
    SELECT Station_ID, COUNT(*) as Total_Trains
    FROM train_station
    GROUP BY Station_ID
  ) as Max_Trains
);
```

-------------------------6619 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.Name
FROM station s
WHERE s.Station_ID IN (
  SELECT ts.Station_ID
  FROM train_station ts
  JOIN train t ON ts.Train_ID = t.Train_ID
  WHERE t.Name IN ('Ananthapuri Express', 'Guruvayur Express')
  GROUP BY ts.Station_ID
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT t.Name) = 2
);
```

FROM Faculty F
JOIN Faculty_Participates_in FP ON F.FacID = FP.FacID

JOIN Student S ON P.stuid = S.StuID
GROUP BY F.FacID;

-------------------------6759 sample_num
```sql
SELECT F.Lname, F.Fname
FROM Faculty F
WHERE (F.FacID, COUNT(S.StuID)) IN (
    SELECT FacID, COUNT(S.StuID)
    FROM Student S
    JOIN Participates_in PI ON S.StuID = PI.stuid
    GROUP BY FacID
    ORDER BY COUNT(S.StuID) DESC
    LIMIT 1
);
```

LIMIT 1;

FROM Faculty
WHERE FacID IN (
  SELECT FacID
  FROM Faculty_Participates_in
  WHERE actid IN (
    SELECT actid
    FROM Activity
    WHERE actid IN (
      SELECT actid
      FROM Participates_in
      WHERE stuid IN (
        SELECT StuID
        FROM Student
        WHERE Advisor IN (
          SELECT FacID
          FROM Faculty
        )
      )
    )
  )
)

)

-------------------------6868 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    a.country,
    a.name AS airline,
    COUNT(*) AS total_routes
FROM
    routes r
INNER JOIN
    airlines a ON r.alid = a.alid
INNER JOIN
    airports dst ON r.dst_apid = dst.apid
INNER JOIN
    airports src ON r.src_apid = src.apid
GROUP BY
    a.country, a.name
```

-------------------------6883 sample_num
```sql
SELECT a.name, COUNT(*) as num_routes
FROM routes r
JOIN airports dst_ap ON r.dst_apid = dst_ap.apid
JOIN airports src_ap ON r.src_apid = src_ap.apid
WHERE dst_ap.country = 'China' OR src_ap.country = 'China'
GROUP BY a.name
ORDER BY num_routes DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

WHERE Stadium_ID NOT IN (
    SELECT Stadium_ID
    FROM concert
    WHERE Year = 2014
)
```
-------------------------7033 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    c.concert_Name,
    c.Theme,
    COUNT(si.Singer_ID) AS Num_Singers
FROM
    concert c
JOIN
    singer_in_concert si ON c.concert_ID = si.concert_ID
GROUP BY
    c.concert_Name,
    c.Theme;
```
-------------------------7034 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    c.concert_Name,
    c.Theme,
    COUNT(s.Singer_ID) AS Num_of_singers
FROM
    concert c
JOIN
    singer_in_concert sic ON c.concert_ID = sic.concert_ID
JOIN
    singer s ON sic.Singer_ID = s.Singer_ID
GROUP BY
    c.concert_Name,
    c.Theme;

SELECT Model
FROM model_list
WHERE ModelId IN (
  SELECT MakeId
  FROM car_names
  WHERE MakeId IN (
    SELECT Id
    FROM car_makers
    WHERE Country IN (
      SELECT CountryName
      FROM countries
      WHERE Continent IN (
        SELECT Continent
        FROM continents
      )
    )
  )
)
ORDER BY Horsepower ASC
LIMIT 1;

SELECT DISTINCT ml.Model
FROM model_list ml
JOIN car_names cn ON ml.Maker = cn.MakeId
JOIN car_makers cm ON cn.MakeId = cm.Id
WHERE cm.FullName IN ('General Motors') AND cars_data.Weight > 3500;
```
-------------------------7152 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT m.Model
FROM model_list m
JOIN car_makers c ON m.Maker = c.Id
WHERE c.Maker = 'General Motors' OR c.Weight > 3500;
```
-------------------------7153 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT Year
FROM cars_data
WHERE Weight BETWEEN 3000 AND 4000;
```
-------------------------7154 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT Year
FROM cars_data
WHERE Weight < 4000 OR Weight > 3000;
```
-------------------------7155 sample_num

FROM cars_data
ORDER BY Accelerate DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------7156 sample_num
```sql
SELECT Horsepower
FROM cars_data
ORDER BY Accelerate DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------7157 sample_num
```sql
SELECT Cylinders
FROM cars_data
WHERE MakeId IN (
  SELECT MakeId
  FROM car_names
  WHERE Model = 'volvo'
) AND Accelerate = (
  SELECT MIN(Accelerate)
  FROM cars_data
  WHERE MakeId IN (
    SELECT MakeId
    FROM car_names
    WHERE Model = 'volvo'
  )
);
```
-------------------------7158 sample_num
```sql
SELECT cylinders
FROM cars_data
WHERE make = (SELECT makeId FROM car_names WHERE model = 'Volvo' AND make = (SELECT Id FROM car_makers WHERE maker = 'Volvo'))
ORDER BY accelerate
LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------7161 sample_num
```sql
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT c.CountryName)
FROM countries c
JOIN car_makers cm ON c.CountryId = cm.Country
GROUP BY c.CountryName
HAVING COUNT(cm.Maker) > 2;
```

  HAVING COUNT(*) > 2

-------------------------7165 sample_num
```sql
SELECT Model
FROM car_names
JOIN model_list ON car_names.MakeId = model_list.ModelId
JOIN car_makers ON model_list.Maker = car_makers.Id
JOIN cars_data ON car_names.MakeId = cars_data.Id
WHERE Cylinders = 4
ORDER BY Horsepower DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------7166 sample_num
```sql
SELECT model_list.Model
FROM model_list
JOIN cars_data ON model_list.ModelId = cars_data.Id
WHERE cars_data.Cylinders = 4
ORDER BY cars_data.Horsepower DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------7167 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.MakeId, cn.Make
FROM car_names cn
JOIN (
  SELECT MakeId
  FROM cars_data
  WHERE Horsepower > (
    SELECT MIN(Horsepower)
    FROM cars_data
  )
  AND Cylinders <= 3
) cd ON cn.MakeId = cd.MakeId
```
-------------------------7168 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.MakeId, cn.Model, cm.Maker
FROM car_names cn
JOIN model_list ml ON cn.Model = ml.Model
JOIN car_makers cm ON ml.Maker = cm.Id
JOIN cars_data cd ON cn.MakeId = cd.Id
WHERE cd.Horsepower > (SELECT MIN(Horsepower) FROM cars_data)
AND cd.Cylinders < 4;
```
-------------------------7169 sample_num

FROM cars_data
WHERE Cylinders = 8 OR Year < 1980;
```
-------------------------7170 sample_num

-------------------------7171 sample_num
```sql
SELECT Model
FROM car_names
JOIN model_list ON car_names.MakeId = model_list.ModelId
JOIN car_makers ON model_list.Maker = car_makers.Maker
WHERE car_makers.FullName != 'Ford Motor Company'
AND car_names.MakeId IN (
  SELECT MakeId
  FROM car_names
  JOIN cars_data ON car_names.Model = cars_data.Id
  WHERE Weight < 3500
)
```
-------------------------7172 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT ml.Model
FROM model_list ml
JOIN car_makers cm ON ml.Maker = cm.Id
JOIN car_names cn ON ml.Maker = cn.MakeId
JOIN cars_data cd ON cn.Model = cd.Id
WHERE cd.Weight < 3500 AND cm.Maker NOT LIKE '%Ford%';
```
-------------------------7173 sample_num

FROM countries c
WHERE c.CountryId NOT IN (
  SELECT c.CountryId
  FROM car_makers c
  GROUP BY c.CountryId
  HAVING COUNT(c.Id) > 0
);

-------------------------7175 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.Id, c.Maker
FROM car_makers c
GROUP BY c.Id, c.Maker
HAVING COUNT(c.Maker) >= 2 AND COUNT(DISTINCT c.Maker) > 3;
```
-------------------------7176 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.Id, c.Maker
FROM car_makers c
JOIN (
  SELECT Maker
  FROM model_list
  GROUP BY Maker
  HAVING COUNT(*) >= 2
) m ON c.Maker = m.Maker
JOIN (
  SELECT MakeId
  FROM car_names
  GROUP BY MakeId
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 3
) n ON c.Id = n.MakeId
```
-------------------------7177 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.CountryId, c.CountryName
FROM countries c
WHERE c.CountryId IN (
  SELECT c.Maker
  FROM car_makers c
  GROUP BY c.Maker
  HAVING COUNT(c.Maker) > 3
)
OR c.CountryName IN (
  SELECT cn.Make
  FROM car_names cn
  WHERE cn.Model = 'fiat'
  GROUP BY cn.Make
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT cn.Model) > 0
);
```
-------------------------7178 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.CountryId, c.CountryName
FROM countries c
WHERE c.CountryId IN (
  SELECT c.CountryId
  FROM car_makers cm
  GROUP BY cm.CountryId
  HAVING COUNT(*) > 3
)
UNION
SELECT c.CountryId, c.CountryName
FROM countries c
JOIN model_list ml ON c.CountryId = ml.Country
WHERE ml.Maker = 'Fiat';
```

-------------------------7221 sample_num
```sql
SELECT airports.City, COUNT(*) as TotalFlights
FROM flights
JOIN airports ON flights.DestAirport = airports.AirportCode
GROUP BY airports.City
ORDER BY TotalFlights DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------7222 sample_num
```sql
SELECT a.City, COUNT(*) as Frequency
FROM flights f
JOIN airports da ON f.DestAirport = da.AirportCode
JOIN airports sa ON f.SourceAirport = sa.AirportCode
JOIN airports a ON da.CountryAbbrev = a.CountryAbbrev
GROUP BY a.City
ORDER BY Frequency DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

```sql
SELECT a.Abbreviation, a.Country
FROM airlines a
JOIN (
  SELECT Airline, COUNT(*) as num_flights
  FROM flights
  GROUP BY Airline
  ORDER BY num_flights LIMIT 1
) f ON a.uid = f.Airline;
