-------------------------7237 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT a.Airline
FROM airlines a
JOIN flights f ON a.uid = f.Airline
WHERE f.SourceAirport = 'APG' OR f.DestAirport = 'APG'
AND f.SourceAirport = 'CVO' OR f.DestAirport = 'CVO';
```
-------------------------7238 sample_num
```sql
SELECT a.Abbreviation
FROM airlines a
WHERE EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM flights f
  WHERE f.Airline = a.uid
  AND f.SourceAirport = 'APG'
)
AND EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM flights f
  WHERE f.Airline = a.uid
  AND f.SourceAirport = 'CVO'
)
```
-------------------------7239 sample_num
```sql
SELECT *
FROM airlines
WHERE EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM flights
  WHERE flights.Airline = airlines.uid
  AND flights.SourceAirport = 'CVO'
)
AND NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1
  FROM flights
  WHERE flights.Airline = airlines.uid
  AND flights.SourceAirport = 'APG'
);
```
-------------------------7240 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT a.Airline
FROM airlines a
WHERE a.uid IN (
  SELECT f.Airline
  FROM flights f
  WHERE f.SourceAirport = 'CVO'
)
AND a.uid NOT IN (
  SELECT f.Airline
  FROM flights f
  WHERE f.SourceAirport = 'APG'
);
```
-------------------------7241 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT a.uid, a.Airline, a.Abbreviation, a.Country
FROM airlines a
JOIN flights f ON a.Airline = f.Airline
GROUP BY a.uid, a.Airline, a.Abbreviation, a.Country
HAVING COUNT(f.FlightNo) >= 10;
```
-------------------------7242 sample_num
```sql
SELECT a.Uid, a.Airline, a.Abbreviation, a.Country
FROM airlines a
JOIN (
  SELECT Airline
  FROM flights
  GROUP BY Airline
  HAVING COUNT(*) >= 10
) f ON a.Uid = f.Airline;
```

-------------------------7257 sample_num
```sql
SELECT a.AirportName
FROM airports a
WHERE a.AirportCode NOT IN (
  SELECT f.SourceAirport FROM flights f
  UNION
  SELECT f.DestAirport FROM flights f
)
AND a.AirportCode NOT IN (
  SELECT a2.AirportCode FROM airports a2
)
```
-------------------------7258 sample_num
```sql
SELECT DISTINCT airports.City, airports.AirportCode, airports.AirportName
FROM airports
WHERE AirportCode NOT IN (
  SELECT SourceAirport FROM flights
  UNION
  SELECT DestAirport FROM flights
)
AND airports.CountryAbbrev IN (
  SELECT CountryAbbrev FROM airlines
)
```

-------------------------7287 sample_num

```sql
SELECT s.Name, COUNT(h.Employee_ID) AS Number_of_employees
FROM hiring h
JOIN shop s ON h.Shop_ID = s.Shop_ID
GROUP BY s.Name;
```
-------------------------7288 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.Name, COUNT(e.Employee_ID) AS Number_of_Employees
FROM shop s
JOIN hiring h ON s.Shop_ID = h.Shop_ID
JOIN employee e ON h.Employee_ID = e.Employee_ID
GROUP BY s.Name;
```

-------------------------7311 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    t.Template_ID,
    rt.Template_Type_Code
FROM
    Templates t
JOIN
    Documents d ON t.Template_ID = d.Template_ID
JOIN
    Ref_Template_Types rt ON t.Template_Type_Code = rt.Template_Type_Code
GROUP BY
    t.Template_ID,
    rt.Template_Type_Code
ORDER BY
    COUNT(d.Document_ID) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------7312 sample_num
```sql
SELECT T.Template_ID, RT.Template_Type_Code
FROM Templates T
JOIN Documents D ON T.Template_ID = D.Template_ID
JOIN Ref_Template_Types RT ON T.Template_Type_Code = RT.Template_Type_Code
GROUP BY T.Template_ID, RT.Template_Type_Code
ORDER BY COUNT(D.Document_ID) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------7313 sample_num
```sql
SELECT Templates.Template_ID
FROM Templates
WHERE Template_ID IN (
  SELECT Templates.Template_ID
  FROM Templates
  JOIN Documents ON Templates.Template_ID = Documents.Template_ID
  GROUP BY Templates.Template_ID
  HAVING COUNT(Documents.Document_ID) > 1
)
```

-------------------------7333 sample_num

```sql
FROM Ref_Template_Types rt
WHERE rt.Template_Type_Code NOT IN (
  SELECT t.Template_Type_Code
  FROM Templates t
  GROUP BY t.Template_Type_Code
  HAVING COUNT(t.Template_ID) >= 3
);
```

```sql
FROM Ref_Template_Types rt

  SELECT 1
  FROM Templates t

  GROUP BY t.Template_Type_Code
  HAVING COUNT(t.Template_ID) >= 3
)
```

```sql

    rtt.Template_Type_Code,
    COUNT(DISTINCT d.Document_ID) AS Num_Documents
FROM
    Ref_Template_Types rtt
INNER JOIN
    Templates t ON rtt.Template_Type_Code = t.Template_Type_Code
INNER JOIN
    Documents d ON t.Template_ID = d.Template_ID
GROUP BY
    rtt.Template_Type_Code
```

-------------------------7343 sample_num
```sql

  RTT.Template_Type_Code,
  COUNT(DISTINCT D.Document_ID) AS Total_Documents
FROM
  Ref_Template_Types RTT

  JOIN Documents D ON T.Template_ID = D.Template_ID
GROUP BY
  RTT.Template_Type_Code
ORDER BY
  Total_Documents DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

```sql
FROM Ref_Template_Types RT
```

```sql
  SELECT 1
  FROM Templates T

    FROM Documents D
    WHERE D.Template_ID = T.Template_ID
  )
)
```

```sql
SELECT Museum_ID, Name
FROM museum
WHERE Museum_ID IN (
  SELECT Museum_ID
  FROM museum
  ORDER BY Num_of_Staff DESC
  LIMIT 1
)
```

-------------------------7419 sample_num
```sql
SELECT v.ID, v.Name, v.Age
FROM visitor v
JOIN visit vi ON v.ID = vi.visitor_ID
GROUP BY v.ID, v.Name, v.Age
HAVING COUNT(vi.Museum_ID) > 1;
```

-------------------------7420 sample_num
```sql
SELECT v.ID, v.Name, v.Level_of_membership
FROM visitor v
JOIN visit vi ON v.ID = vi.visitor_ID
WHERE vi.Total_spent = (
  SELECT MAX(Total_spent)
  FROM visit
);
```
-------------------------7421 sample_num
```sql
SELECT m.Museum_ID, m.Name
FROM museum m
JOIN (
  SELECT Museum_ID, COUNT(*) as count
  FROM visit
  GROUP BY Museum_ID
  ORDER BY count DESC
  LIMIT 1
) v ON m.Museum_ID = v.Museum_ID;
```

-------------------------7426 sample_num
```sql
SELECT v.Name
FROM visitor v
JOIN visit vi ON v.ID = vi.visitor_ID
JOIN museum m ON vi.Museum_ID = m.Museum_ID
WHERE m.Open_Year < 2009 OR m.Open_Year > 2011
GROUP BY v.Name
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT m.Open_Year) = 2;
```

-------------------------7451 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.country_code, p.first_name
FROM players p
WHERE p.player_id IN (
  SELECT m.loser_id
  FROM matches m
  WHERE m.tourney_name = 'WTA Championships' AND m.winner_id = m.loser_id
  UNION
  SELECT m.winner_id
  FROM matches m
  WHERE m.tourney_name = 'Australian Open' AND m.winner_id = m.loser_id
);
```

```sql
  AND m.winner_id IN (
    SELECT r.player_id
    FROM rankings r
    WHERE r.ranking = 'WTA Champion' OR r.ranking = 'Australian Open Champion'
  )
)
```

-------------------------7463 sample_num
```sql
SELECT w.first_name, w.winner_rank_points
FROM (
  SELECT winner_id, COUNT(*) as win_count
  FROM matches
  GROUP BY winner_id
  ORDER BY win_count DESC
  LIMIT 1
) AS winner
JOIN players w ON winner.winner_id = w.player_id;
```

```sql
LIMIT 3;
```

-------------------------7488 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.first_name, p.country_code, p.birth_date
FROM players p
JOIN (
  SELECT winner_id, SUM(winner_rank_points) AS total_winner_rank_points
  FROM matches
  GROUP BY winner_id
  ORDER BY total_winner_rank_points DESC
  LIMIT 1
) AS winner_rank_points ON p.player_id = winner_rank_points.winner_id;
```

```sql
FROM battle b
```

```sql
  SELECT caused_by_ship_id, COUNT(id) AS total_killed
  FROM death

) d ON b.id = d.caused_by_ship_id
```

```sql
) t ON s.semester_id = t.semester_id
```

-------------------------7533 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
  s.first_name,
  s.middle_name,
  s.last_name,
  se.degree_program_id
FROM
  Students s
  JOIN Student_Enrolment se ON s.student_id = se.student_id
  JOIN Semesters sm ON se.semester_id = sm.semester_id
WHERE
  se.degree_program_id IN (
    SELECT
      degree_program_id
    FROM
      Student_Enrolment
    GROUP BY
      degree_program_id
    HAVING
      COUNT(DISTINCT degree_program_id) = 2
  )
  AND sm.semester_name = 'your semester name';
```
-------------------------7534 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    s.student_id,
    s.first_name,
    s.middle_name,
    s.last_name
FROM
    Students s
JOIN
    Student_Enrolment se ON s.student_id = se.student_id
JOIN
    Degree_Programs dp ON se.degree_program_id = dp.degree_program_id
JOIN
    Semesters sm ON se.semester_id = sm.semester_id
GROUP BY
    s.student_id,
    s.first_name,
    s.middle_name,
    s.last_name
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT dp.degree_program_id) = 2;
```

-------------------------7541 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.student_id, s.first_name, s.middle_name, s.last_name, COUNT(se.degree_program_id) as num_enrollments
FROM Students s
JOIN Student_Enrolment se ON s.student_id = se.student_id
GROUP BY s.student_id, s.first_name, s.middle_name, s.last_name
ORDER BY num_enrollments DESC
LIMIT 1;
```
-------------------------7542 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    s.student_id,
    s.first_name,
    s.middle_name,
    s.last_name,
    COUNT(se.student_enrolment_id) AS num_enrollments
FROM
    Students s
JOIN
    Student_Enrolment se ON s.student_id = se.student_id
GROUP BY
    s.student_id, s.first_name, s.middle_name, s.last_name
ORDER BY
    num_enrollments DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------7546 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.course_name
FROM Student_Enrolment_Courses sec
JOIN Courses c ON sec.course_id = c.course_id
WHERE sec.course_id IN (
  SELECT sc.course_id
  FROM Student_Enrolment se
  JOIN Student_Enrolment_Courses sc ON se.student_enrolment_id = sc.student_enrolment_id
  GROUP BY sc.course_id
  HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT se.student_id) > 0
);
```

-------------------------7551 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    t.transcript_date,
    t.transcript_id
FROM
    Transcripts t
JOIN
    Transcript_Contents tc ON t.transcript_id = tc.transcript_id
GROUP BY
    t.transcript_id, t.transcript_date
HAVING
    COUNT(tc.student_course_id) >= 2;
```

-------------------------7557 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.first_name, s.middle_name, s.last_name
FROM Students s
JOIN Student_Enrolment se ON s.student_id = se.student_id
JOIN Transcripts t ON se.degree_program_id = t.transcript_id
WHERE se.date_enrolled = (SELECT MIN(date_enrolled) FROM Student_Enrolment);
```
-------------------------7558 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
    s.first_name,
    s.middle_name,
    s.last_name
FROM
    Students s
JOIN
    Student_Enrolment se ON s.student_id = se.student_id
JOIN
    Student_Enrolment_Courses sec ON se.student_enrolment_id = sec.student_enrolment_id
JOIN
    Transcripts t ON sec.student_course_id = t.student_course_id
JOIN
    Transcript_Contents tc ON t.transcript_id = tc.transcript_id
ORDER BY
    t.transcript_date ASC
LIMIT 1;
```

```sql
LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------7571 sample_num

```sql
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT tc.transcript_id), sce.student_course_id
FROM Transcript_Contents tc
JOIN Student_Enrolment_Courses sce ON tc.student_course_id = sce.student_course_id
GROUP BY sce.student_course_id
ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT tc.transcript_id) DESC;
```
-------------------------7572 sample_num
```sql
SELECT
  COUNT(tc.student_course_id) AS max_count,
  se.student_enrolment_id AS enrollment_id
FROM
  Transcript_Contents tc
  JOIN Student_Enrolment_Courses sec ON tc.student_course_id = sec.student_course_id
  JOIN Student_Enrolment se ON sec.student_enrolment_id = se.student_enrolment_id
GROUP BY
  se.student_enrolment_id
ORDER BY
  COUNT(tc.student_course_id) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

```sql
ORDER BY

LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------7575 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.semester_name
FROM Student_Enrolment se
JOIN Students s ON se.student_id = s.student_id
JOIN Degree_Programs dp ON se.degree_program_id = dp.degree_program_id
WHERE dp.degree_summary_name IN ('Master', 'Bachelor')
GROUP BY s.semester_name
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT dp.degree_summary_name) = 2;
```
-------------------------7576 sample_num
```sql
SELECT s.semester_id
FROM Student_Enrolment se
JOIN Degree_Programs dp ON se.degree_program_id = dp.degree_program_id
JOIN Students s ON se.student_id = s.student_id
WHERE dp.degree_summary_name IN ('Masters', 'Bachelors')
GROUP BY s.semester_id
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT dp.degree_summary_name) = 2;
```

-------------------------7694 sample_num
```sql
SELECT c.contestant_number, c.contestant_name
FROM CONTESTANTS c
JOIN VOTES v ON c.contestant_number = v.contestant_number
GROUP BY c.contestant_number, c.contestant_name
HAVING COUNT(v.vote_id) >= 2;
```
-------------------------7695 sample_num

```sql
FROM CONTESTANTS C
WHERE C.contestant_number IN (
  SELECT V.contestant_number
  FROM VOTES V
  GROUP BY V.contestant_number
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) ASC
  LIMIT 1
)
```

-------------------------7700 sample_num
```sql
SELECT distinct A.area_code
FROM VOTES V
JOIN CONTESTANTS C ON V.contestant_number = C.contestant_number
JOIN AREA_CODE_STATE A ON V.state = A.state
WHERE C.contestant_name IN ('Tabatha Gehling', 'Kelly Clauss')
GROUP BY A.area_code
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT V.contestant_number) = 2;
```

-------------------------7890 sample_num
```sql
SELECT name
FROM Highschooler, Friend
WHERE Highschooler.ID = Friend.student_id
AND Highschooler.name != 'Kyle'
AND Friend.friend_id IN (SELECT student_id FROM Friend WHERE student_id IN (SELECT ID FROM Highschooler WHERE name = 'Kyle'));
```

```sql
  SELECT f2.name
  FROM Highschooler AS h2
  JOIN Friend AS f2 ON h2.ID = f2.student_id
  WHERE h2.name = 'Kyle'
);
```

```sql
FROM Professionals p
WHERE p.state = 'Indiana'
   OR (p.professional_id IN (
       SELECT t.professional_id
       FROM Treatments t
       GROUP BY t.professional_id
       HAVING COUNT(t.treatment_id) > 2
   ));
```

-------------------------7924 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.name
FROM Dogs d
WHERE d.dog_id NOT IN (
  SELECT t.dog_id
  FROM Treatments t
  JOIN Charges c ON t.cost_of_treatment = c.charge_amount
  WHERE c.charge_type = 'Treatment'
  GROUP BY t.dog_id
  HAVING SUM(c.charge_amount) > 1000
)
```
-------------------------7925 sample_num
```sql
SELECT d.name
FROM Dogs d
JOIN Owners o ON d.owner_id = o.owner_id
JOIN Treatments t ON d.dog_id = t.dog_id
WHERE o.owner_id IN (
  SELECT o.owner_id
  FROM Owners o
  LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT dog_id, SUM(cost_of_treatment) AS total_cost
    FROM Treatments
    GROUP BY dog_id
  ) t ON o.owner_id = t.dog_id
  WHERE t.total_cost <= 1000
)
```

-------------------------7936 sample_num
```sql
SELECT o.owner_id, o.last_name
FROM Owners o
JOIN (
  SELECT dog_id, COUNT(*) as total_treatments
  FROM Treatments
  GROUP BY dog_id
) t ON o.owner_id = t.dog_id
JOIN (
  SELECT dog_id, COUNT(*) as total_treatments
  FROM Treatments
  GROUP BY dog_id
  ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC
  LIMIT 1
) max_treatments ON o.owner_id = max_treatments.dog_id
```
-------------------------7937 sample_num

```sql
  GROUP BY dog_id
  ORDER BY total_cost DESC
  LIMIT 1
) t ON o.owner_id = t.dog_id
```

```sql
FROM Treatment_Types
WHERE treatment_type_code = (
  SELECT treatment_type_code
  FROM Treatments
  GROUP BY treatment_type_code
  ORDER BY SUM(cost_of_treatment) ASC
  LIMIT 1
);
```
-------------------------7939 sample_num
```sql

FROM Treatments t1
JOIN Treatment_Types t2 ON t1.treatment_type_code = t2.treatment_type_code
GROUP BY t2.treatment_type_description
ORDER BY SUM(t1.cost_of_treatment) ASC
LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------7940 sample_num

```sql
FROM Owners o
JOIN Dogs d ON o.owner_id = d.owner_id

ORDER BY SUM(c.charge_amount) DESC
LIMIT 1;
```

-------------------------7941 sample_num
```sql
SELECT o.owner_id, o.zip_code
FROM Owners o
JOIN (
  SELECT owner_id, SUM(c.charge_amount) AS total_spent
  FROM Charges c
  JOIN Dogs d ON c.charge_id = d.owner_id
  GROUP BY owner_id
  ORDER BY total_spent DESC
  LIMIT 1
) t ON o.owner_id = t.owner_id
```

```sql
);
```

-------------------------8033 sample_num
```sql
SELECT p.property_name
FROM Properties p
WHERE p.property_type_code IN (
  SELECT rt.property_type_code
  FROM Ref_Property_Types rt
  WHERE rt.property_type_description IN ('House', 'Apartment')
)
AND p.room_count > 1;
```
